reviews.text:
"Salmon Tepanyaki"
The food taste very good, the servant is very kind. This restaurant have a great ambience , and the price is pretty affordable for the great food
reviews.title: Dinner with Family

reviews.text:
We booked on teppanyaki table in front of the chef that will cook live and serve you directly. We ordered seafood teppanyaki set with snapper, prawn, scallop, veggies, fried rice, miso soup, salmon, and ice cream on banana as dessert. With the set there is plenty of food, so better not order extra.
The chefs are skillful and will put out a show with their cooking tools. Very attractive! They also will politely asked if you are ready for next dish.
Try the green tea (ocha, served cold or hot), fresh and free flow.
The teppanyaki table can be full, so recommend to book first.
reviews.title: Great food, friendly and demonstrative chefs

reviews.text:
Very satisfied with the food and service there. 
Just try the Giant yakimeshi with very cheap price and tazmania volcano which so melted in my mouth !
reviews.title: Cozy place and various food

reviews.text:
the taste was very nice and I am very satisfied, chef will cook in front of you and nice flame cooking attraction

The portion is not too big but it's very more than enough for fine dining
Price about 250.000++ and it is located inside Blue Sky Hotel Balikpapan
reviews.title: great Tepanyaki ever and You must try if visit Balikpapan

reviews.text: My kids love it and we always go there for Sunday lunch. The teppanyaki grill is very good and it's a pyrotechnic show. The shabu-shabu is also good.
reviews.title: Best teppanyaki grill in Balikpapan

reviews.text: Ho mangiato in questo ristorante in quanto soggiornavo al Blue Sky Hotel. Abbiamo preso il teppanyaki con salmone, gamberi e filetto di manzo ed era davvero buono! Chef molto bravo che faceva giochi con il fuoco. Abbiamo preso anche degli uramaki, che per non erano niente di speciale. In definitiva consigliato per il teppanyaki, prezzo alto per lIndonesia, ma contenuto per lItalia, circa 30 a testa per mangiare a volont.
reviews.title: Molto buono

reviews.text:
Penyajian termasuk lama untuk shabu shabu dan ramen (saya menunggu 2 jam), menu lain normal (sushi , tepanyaki),
Saya menemukan kecoak hidup di tutup mangkuk kuah shabu shabu, untungnya langsung diganti.
Untuk kelas restauran di hotel, termasuk harus diimprove banyak terutama hygienitas dan pelayanan.
Tempatnya nyaman dan cukup baik 
Jika pesan Tepanyaki ada bonus atraksi kokinya, ini yang sepertinya membuat pelayanan untuk yang non tepanyaki menjadi lama, kokinya hanya ada 1 orang.
Harga cukup premium.
reviews.title: Bad experience...

owner_response.text:
Tamu As D yang terhormat,

Salam Hangat dari Blue Sky Hotel Balikpapan..

Terima kasih atas komentar yang diberikan, dan kami sangat menyesalkan kejadian tersebut. Manajer Restoran kami sudah menindaklanjuti permasalahan yang terjadi, da sudah melakukan investigasi kepada staff yang in charge pada saat itu.

Kami berkomitmen hal tersebut tidak akan terulang kembali di kemudian hari, dan besar harapan kami untuk dapat menyambut kedatangannya kembali di restoran dan hotel Blue Sky Hotel Balikpapan.

Silakan langsung menghubungi Manajer kami untuk bantuan selanjutnya. Terima kasih atas perhatiannya.

Salam,
Renny Margaretha
Public Relations Manager

reviews.text: Kemarin saya mencoba promo terbaru di kaezeki restaurant , rasanya ssngat enak dan harganya terjangkau disertai dengan service yang memuaskan , sangat recomended
reviews.title: Dinner

rekomen untuk anda pecinta tepanyaki,Salmon soup, dan bento,

Saya sarankan ke teppanyakinya.., karena akan ada chef yang akan ngasi live cooking entertainment . Dari menu appetizer sampai dessert akan disajikan dengan atraksi yang menarik. Dan bukan sekedar menarik saja, tapi rasanya juga enyakk banget !! Nah favorite saya adalah tuna yang diolah antar digoreng dan dibakar trus di tuangin saus beghhh lezatnyaaa. belum lagi soup tofunyaa hangat dan sedapp. Pokoknya kita ga bakalan kecewa dah. Biar berlama-lama disini juga gpp karena mata kita terhibur melihat atraksi chef yang melemparkan spatula, pisau, salt and papper shacker ke udara saat memasak itu bukanlah pertunjukan biasa karena pasti butuh latihan dan jam terbang tinggi. Untuk harga...hemmm jangan ditanya yach sudah psti MAHAL per pax nya hahaha. So tapi worthy lah untuk sensasi yang kita dapatkan..

name: Pasta Cielo
address: Jln. Jendral Sudirman No. 47 In shops surrounding E-Walk Plaza, Balikpapan 76112 Indonesia

reviews.text:
Me and my other managers have been about one year trying different (business) lunches around town ( Balikpapan Indonesia).  We've have finally come to the conclusion that Pasta Cielo is the hands down winner in this town.  Food quality is excellent.  Starters come first, entrees' come second and so on.  Not like other restaurants in this town where it seems that delivery is very random and out of order.  The half roast Chicken, tacos, salads, soups all excellent.  Me and my managers confirm that Pasta Cielo is hands down the winner.  highly recommended for a good business lunch or dinner. 
(i think there isn't any wine but we only eat there for lunch so maybe if you go for dinner you must BYOB)
reviews.title: Finally a restaurant in Balikpapan that knows what they are doing

reviews.text:
Restaurant with many choices, both asian & western. The service was fast and good and the prices reasonable. The tenderloin was delicious.

reviews.text: We have ate here 4 or 5 times every time the food was perfect. The staff are very helpful and always looking to help. The only thing I would say, the restaurant is not always busy and there is more staff thank customer and they are standing or sitting around doing than nothing. Take away food is excellent, the packing of the food is great. Overall a great restaurant with great food. reviews.text:
The only restaurant that keeps in standard in balikpapan. Comparable to 4 stars hotel's restaurant. I never have any single complaints against the food, the waitress, the server! The mexican food is 10 out of 10. Steak is 7 out of 10. The ribs is 8 out of 10. And the pasta - our favourite will be the homemade shredded beef cooked al dente spaghety. Kids love it.

Not for coffee lover. Skip the coffee menu and go to juice option instead.

reviews.text:
The pasta at this restaurant is undoubtedly worthy of your visit. 

The ambiance is quite homey. There's no odd smells or anything that can turn you off. The place itself is quite new since they had just relocate from the base of the nearby mall. They said that the restaurant has been established for more than 5 years. 

The staffs are quite friendly and helpful. I had to put my credit card with them so that I could pay for the group, since we are usually fighting to pay for the bills at the end. The staff understood it immediately and being helpful overall in making sure that there's no stray payment other than mine. 

I'd recommend the lasagna. It's very delicious! Other pasta is amazing as well. 

I haven't try the dessert so I can't comment on that yet. The drinks are also quite interesting and varied.

must try in Balikpapan!
reviews.title: Amazing pasta! Friendly staffs

reviews.text:

reviews.text: I rarely found a proper place to eat pasta outside Java. This place is recommended! The price around 80-150 k per person. But it taste good and the quality is undoubted.
reviews.title: Great atmosphere with tasty food

reviews.text:
We were in Balikpapan on vacation, and had had Pasta Cielo recommended to us by a friend who had also eaten there before.  They obviously serve Italian, which seemed to be pretty good, and is actually pretty rare in the area.  But the real surprise was that they also served Mexican!  The beef and chicken fajitas are excellent, considering you are eating in South East Asia.  The tortillas were nice and fluffy, and served warm.  The meat was seasoned very nicely, and they were accompanied by a garnish similar to pico de gallo, but made from local ingredients. (The local name is dabu-dabu, and it's pretty similar) There was also grated cheese, guacamole (avocado grows locally) and sour cream the first time we went, but when we went back later in the week they were out of sour cream.  They did apologize, though!  

The service was very good, and they were attentive and helpful.  We showed up as a family of five, and we were welcomed and they re-arranged several two-tops to accommodate us.  Also, some of our family have a milk allergy, and they were willing and able to prepare dishes without dairy.  Sometimes that's a struggle to get them to adjust here in the area, but it was no problem for the staff here.  

The restaurant itself is inside the shopping center with the E-Walk Mall, but it was quiet both times we went.  The prices are more than you would pay in a food stall, but fall in line with what you would pay in the better restaurants elsewhere in the shopping center.  Definitely not out of reach by western standards.
reviews.title: A nice surprise, great food, great place!

reviews.text: I don't agree when most of people say it taste good. I was born in makssar & to say it taste good is far from the original taste in makssasar. reviews.text:
This place is in a hidden alley next to BCA Bank, not a big restaurant but let's called it like small warung still when you get there after 12PM in the afternoon, dont hope to much you could taste the famous soup Konro. It has big slice of beef ribs with soup contained of lot of spice and they serve rice all you can eat. The meat is soft when you bite it and so easily to cut into small pieces. They provide menu a traditional South Sulawesi-Makasar such as Sop Saudara, Sop Konro, Sop Jeroan and even Sop Konro Torpedo. Its open from 9.00 up to the stock finished on that day. Do not expected that you could had long chit chat on that place once you finished with your meals, cause many people already make a queue outside the warung
Small tips: better call them first to keep the stock of Sop Konro before you go there especially when youre in big group' (more than 2 persons)
reviews.title: Still the winner

reviews.text: Location of this food stall is hidden between the buildings. It is very crowded during lunch time and don't be sorry if you have to cancel your lunch because they run out of the Sop Konro. So far this is the best sop konro in Balikpapan.

reviews.text: Only a small and not representative eat place, cannot be called restaurant, but this place is legend and so called the best in taste Konro soup in Balikpapan. The taste of the broth is incredible, rich and addicting. The meat itself cooked until it is very tender. With only reasonable price we will get a generous portion of the meat and free broth and rice as you can. But since it is only a small place, better to avoid lunch time to have a relax meal time.
reviews.title: Legendary Konro soup

reviews.text:
Balikpapan is the city in East Borneo, famous with clean and neat city. It is not surprising, because the city was oil rich, and causing people to come from across the country. That's why Balikpapan has no original food, food here are blending from around in Indonesia.
But, you have to try roast seafood in Warung Haur Gading. Fish and prawn were roasted. It is presented with spinach soup and hot chili sauce. Delicious!

Price? not too cheap but not too expensive it is about USD 3 per menu per person (rice, soup, fish)
Place? Awful, this would be better if a bit huge. It toke several time because of queuing too long.
reviews.title: Search for food in Balikpapan? Try Haur Gading

reviews.text: Famous grilled seafood restaurant among Balikpapan locals. Always busy during lunch time. Excellent udang bakar! Pepes patin and patin bakar also very good.

This warung is located at the back end of the famous kebun sayur market.

Reasonably priced too for Balikpapan area.
Worth a visit while you're in town.

reviews.text:
Resto yang menyajikan masakan serba mie ini (walaupun ada juga menu sop daging) menjadi favorit saya sejak lebih dari 20 tahun yang lalu, dan sekarang ada cabangnya juga di Jl. MT. Haryono seberang perumahan Bukit Damai Indah.
Menurut saya, resto ini menyajikan mie ayam dan berbagai variannya dengan rasa yang otentik. Sambalnyapun nendang banget, dan yang istimewa disini cukanya juga khusus, seperti ada gilingan cabe merah di dalamnya. Favorit saya adalah mie bakso campur yang disajikan terpisah, porsi mie polos (tanpa diberi kecap) yang cukup besar disajikan dengan kuah kaldu gurih berisi bakso, potongan kikil, babat, daging dan tahu daging goreng. Sedangkan minuman favorit disini adalah es sari kacang hijau yang harum, manis dan legit. Ada juga menu es shanghai dan es campur yang porsinya cukup besar. 
Harga bervariasi mulai 18.000 - 28.000 per mangkok kalau tidak salah. Dan sekarang enaknya sejak ada ojek online kita juga bisa memesan melalui layanan pembelian makanan online.
reviews.title: Mie ayam favorit

reviews.text: Bakso sapinya berasa daging banget. Harganya memang mahal untuk ukuran baso sapi di balikpapan. Tapi rasa n harga masih sebanding. 1 mangkok mie baso berkisar 30ribuan

reviews.text:
Berdiri sejak tahun 1983.
Terjamin karna semua bahan dibuat sendiri dan tanpa bahan pengawet...
Produk kami yg terpopuler adalah Bakso dan Mie serta minuman Es Sari Kacang Ijo...

reviews.text: pelayanan nya cepat dan ramah, ditambah makanan nya yg enak enak, dan yg penting harga nya terjangkau. hahahaa

reviews.text: Tempat makan ini terletak persis di ruko seberang plaza balikpapan. Menu yg disediakan mcm2 mulai dari mie ayam, yamin, bakso ikan n bakso sapi. Bakso sapinya bisa dibilang salah satu yg paling enak di balikpapan karena berasa sekali dagingnya. Untuk bakso ikannya fresh n lumayan oke. Sambal yg disediakan pun cocok dengan lidah yg suka pedas. Es campurnya enak n ga terlalu manis. Overall bisa dibilang sekali coba pasti akan mau balik lagi kesini..
reviews.title: Baksonya daging banget!

reviews.text: Pangsit mie nya mantap, dari jaman saya kecil sampai sekarang rasa tak pernah berubah. Paling suka mie nya karena tekstur mie nya kecil2. Baksonya juga enak bgt, kerasa daging.
reviews.title: Pangsit Mie Bakso Sapi Mantap

reviews.text: Setiap saya ke balikpapan tempat ini merupakan salah satu tujuan kuliner saya. Selain rasa baksonya yang enak, mie kuning baksonya yang bikin saya gak bisa nahan. Ane paling seneng dengan mie nya, enaknya pake banget biar gak pake bakso ato kuah tetap maknyos. Wajib coba klo k balikpapan.
reviews.title: Sedaappp

reviews.text: Waktu saya dan teman saya menginap di salah satu hotel yang kebetulan tidak jauh dari tempat makan Bakso Sapi,saya dan teman saya penasaran untuk mencobanya,sesampai di tempat tersebut alangkah kagetnya saya karena ruangan atau tempat makan tersebut sangat di penuhi pengunjung yang sedang bersantap Bakso sapi ini,baik yang makan di tempt maupun di bungkus..saya dan teman saya memesan 2 porsi Bakso Sapi ini bersama 2 minuman dingin air mineral,,,tak terasa hidangan pesanan kami datang,,pada saat kami santap Bakso Sapi tersebut kami heran kenapa Bakso sapi ini sangat enak,,mie dan kuah bakso nya juga lezat,,pantas aja ramai di kunjungi orang2.gak percuma dan gak rugi datang ke Bakso Sapi ini,,sudah pelayanan nya cepat,,nikmat pula....
reviews.title: Makan Malam yang tak terlupakan...

reviews.text: O preo  bem barato para Balikpapan, mas o lugar  feio e calorento. A comida nao tem nenhum encanto. Ideal para passar s quando esta com pressa e com fome.
reviews.title: Bakso barato

reviews.text: Depot ini buka nya hanya petang hingga malam hari. Sesuai nama tempatnya, menu andalannya adalah adalah serba bakso .., tapi divariasikan dengan menu lain-lain. Seperti Mie pangsit ..Mie pangsit bakso ikan dll. Oiya coba deh pesan juga krupuk siomay nya.., kriuk banget, sepertinya ga cukup klo pesan 1 porsi ajah. Yang bikin beda mie ini dengan mie diluar adalah bahan mie nya memang dibuat sendiri. jadi bisa lembut dan kenyal. Nah setelah kenyang, jangan lupa pesan es kacang ijo nya..., slurrppp nendang banget !! okeh met wisata kuliner dan tetap sehattt yach kakak !!

reviews.text: Letak Bakso Sapi ini berada di pusat kota Balikpapan, sehingga sangat mudah untuk menemukan warung bakso ini. Saya memesan 1 porsi Bakso. Dan bagi kalian pecinta pecinta bakso pasti akan senang ketika memesan bakso disini. Karena porsi bakso yg mereka sediakan sangat banyak. 1 mangkok besar pasti akan membuat kalian sangat kenyang! Worth to buy!
reviews.title: Porsi jumbo untuk penggemar Bakso!

reviews.text:
Bakso Sapi Pasar Baru terletak di pusat kota dengan letak yang sangat strategis dan mudah dijangkau. Meskipun namanya Bakso Sapi bukan berarti menunya hanya Bakso saja, namun juga terdapat mantau dan nasi goreng. 
Penyajian bakso di sini dipisah antara mie dan kuahnya sehingga dapat memilih sendiri bagaimana kita hendak menikmati bakso tersebut apakah langsung dituang semua atau sedikit demi sedikit.
Menurut saya rasa dari kuah baksonya tidak istimewa, berbeda dengan keterkenalan restoran ini.
reviews.title: Bakso Sapi Pasar Baru

reviews.text: Tempat nya strategis sekali, karena tempat ini pusat belanja serba ada. banyak sekali menu yg tersedia disini, tapi baksonya itu lho yg wow....
reviews.title: Bakso yang tak pernah sepi

name: Rumah Makan Teluk Bayur
address: Jl. Jend. Ahmad Yani, RT. 41 no. 33, Gunung Sari Ilir, Balikpapan Indonesia

reviews.text: First i don't think so that i like seafood,  but when my client take me to this restaurant i think i fall in love with seafood ,  they have a fresh seafood,  we can choose directly to the storage what kind of fish that we want.  The taste was very good.  You must try this restaurant when you visit balikpapan,  the location easy to find out.
reviews.title: Fresh seafood

reviews.text: We order 2 kind of fish and oyster also kangkung. they give 3 kind of sambal that very delicious : green sambal or sambal ijo, sambal with young manggo, and the last is teh best : sambal dabu-dabu ... hmhmm very good taste and also i order for bring home, one fish and one squid. they wrap very well and give me 3 kind of sambal too.. very good
reviews.title: very good taste and fresh seafoods

reviews.text: Honestly, this place is better than Bondi. They have the best seafood here. Fresh and taste amazing. My recommendations? 1. Fried Squid 2. Ikan bakar 3. Fried Enoki.
reviews.title: Best Seafood in Balikpapan

reviews.text:
All the foods is delicious.
We were 4 adults and 1 children ordered grilled fish, grilled squids, chicken satay, and sop buntut. It's also have sensible price. Definitely worth the money if you have big family and friends to eat here.
I recommended this place if you choose quality over the view (i compare Teluk Bayur with oceans restaurant). They gave sayur asem as compliment - very delicious. They got 4 different sambal, if you are sambal lovers this is the place. My favorite is red sambal with salari.

Definitely will come back when i visit Balikpapan.
reviews.title: The best local restaurant

reviews.text: One of the popular seafood restaurant in Balikpapan, yet I always order iridescent fish every time here. The taste of food serve here are good but the price is not so good. They need to rejuvenate the venue.
reviews.title: Good and fresh sea food

reviews.text: Their food was amazing! I had a truly satisfying lunch at the restaurant. The herbs and sauces were perfectly mixed & absorbed into the cuisines. I'm slightly allergic to seafood, and yet couldn't stop eating. Will definitely come back here again when visiting Balikpapan.
reviews.title: Amazingly delicious seafood

reviews.text:
Ke Balikpapan lagi ke RM Teluk Bayur lagi.
Sudah berlangganan dari tahun 90an dmn saat itu masih kecil tempatnya dan harus antri saat akn makan siang, hingga kini sdh sangat besar dan representatif sekali tempatnya.
Kerang sambal gorengnya mantap apalagi diberi pete yg jg mantap.
Kepiting saos lada hitamnya tidak kalah dengan Dandito maupun Kenari yg sdh sangat dikenal di Balikpapan.
Tapi yg pasti harganya lebih murah disini.
reviews.title: Tetap yan terenak

reviews.text: Diajak klien makan siang disini,suasana resto ramai dengan pengunjung,tempat luas dan bersih.Makanan yang dipesan keluar dengan cukup cepat dan rasa semua enak.Ikan bskar kami dilengkapi dengan 4 macam sambal.Udang goreng juga ensk dan sayur kangkung masak terasi patut dicoba.
reviews.title: Resto seafood lama tapi tetap eksis

reviews.text: Rekomendasi sopir sewaan untuk makan di sini dengan rasa masakan yang enak, tempat yang cukup nyaman dengan harga yang tidak terlalu mahal (yang cukup mahal).
reviews.title: Enak meski agak mahal

reviews.text:
Sudah cukup lama tidak pernah mampir ke RM ini, kangen dengan masakan-masakannya, saat ada kesempatan ke Balikpapan lagi saya tidak menyiayiakan kesempatan ini.
Kepiting Lada Hitam langsung saya pesan karena ini favorit saya lagi ditambah beberapa menu lainnya, rasa masakannya masih tetap enak, tidak sia-sia saya menyisihkan waktu ke RM Teluk Bayur.
Pokoknya ini direkomendasikan buat yang sedang ke balikpapan.

reviews.text: Resto ini tempatnya nyaman dengan layanan yang baik dan ramah. Seafoodnya segar dan enak. Tersedia menu Aneka ikan bakar, Aneka ikan goreng, Udang goreng tepung, Udang saos lada hitam, Kepiting asam manis, Sop buntut, Ayam bakar, Ayam goreng dan lainnya. Sop buntut rasanya segar dan nikmat. Ikan goreng rasanya enak dan gurih dengan daging yang lembut. Udang goreng tepung rasanya enak dan gurih.

reviews.text: seafood disini fresh banget dan bisa masak dengan bumbu yang beragam. waktu itu pesan udang yang besar2 dan ikan bakar. untuk harga cukup lumayan sih menurut saya hehe
reviews.title: Seafood fresh, harga cukup lumayan

reviews.text:
Udang galahnya enak dan murah... 
Dijkt 100-150rb/pcs disini  65rb/pcs
Ditambah lagi kerang sama patin2ny the best pokoke
reviews.title: Best price

reviews.text: Lokasi strategis di tengah kota, bahan masakannya fresh terasa saat cicipan pertama. Bumbunya pas rasanya apalagi cocolan sambelnya ada, joss bangaaatt. Ikan nya juga fresh, crispy n crunchy.  Mantap dah pokoknya.
reviews.title: Delicious

reviews.text:
tempat bersih,ruangan besar,kualitas seafood oke..pelayanan ramah dan cepat..
cuma sayangnya tmpt parkirnya susah.apalagi klo dtng pas jam makan siang.bakalan hrs parkir jauh...
reviews.title: lunch with my son

reviews.text: Seafood yang dijual disini masih segar, biasanya kita diminta untuk memilih jenis ikan dan ukuran yang akan diolah, apakah akan di bakar atau digoreng. Setelah itu ditanyain lagi mo dikasi bumbu / saus ga ? seperti asam manis, rica-rica atau balado. Oiyaa ada juga pilihan seafood untuk udang, kerang dan cumi . Nah untuk pilihan menu pendamping lauk seperti terong balado/bakar, petai bakar dan tahu tempe juga bisa kita minta disini. Untuk pilihan sambal nanti akan diberikan beberapa macam sambal sekaligus tinggal kita suka yang mana. Untuk harga memang relative mahal disini, tapi untuk sekali-kali menjamu tamu ataupun makan dengan keluarga it's worthy lah !! Cuman 1 kekurangannya, yaitu parkirannya sulit euy... :(
reviews.title: Seafoodnya juara

reviews.text:
Satu lagi tempat makanan enak di Balikpapan, RM Teluk Bayur. Ga jauh-jauh dari menu seafood, tapi fokusnya ke ikan bakar... Di sini sedia banyak jenis ikan, kita bisa pilih mau ikan apa di kulkas yang tersedia, mau dibakar atau diapakan, mau dengan bumbu apa. Setelah pilih, duduk dan pesan menu lainnya. Saya pesan nasi, calamari (cumi goreng), dan sayuran, plus jus mangga. Calamari-nya ga salah.. enak! renyah dan ga alot... rasanya yummy. Ikan bakarnya saya pilih bumbu dabu-dabu. Dan memang, ikan bakarnya nikmat!!!
Ohya, di sini sudah dapat sayur asam. Jadi, saya agak salah nih pesan sayur lagi...
Untuk harga, lumayan terjangkau, apalagi dengan makanan yang enak, jadi rasanya puas...
Lokasinya di pinggir jalan, dan parkirannya terbatas. Namun, Anda bisa saja naik angkot ke jalan Ahmad Yani no.2 atau 5. Dari luar, bisa saja nama restorannya tidak terlihat, jadi perlu lebih teliti. Namun, tempat makan ini tidak kecil, areanya cukup luas untuk makan bersama keluarga. Tempat makannya agak terbuka.
Selamat makan.. =)
reviews.title: Jagoan Ikan Bakar

reviews.text:
Saya selalu mampir di rumah makan ini setiap kali melakukan perjalanan ke Balikpapan untuk urusan kerja. 
Kenal restaurant ini pertama th 2005 saat pertama kali mengunjungi Balikpapan. Dulu bangunan restaurant ini kecil dan sederhana, menyerupai warteg kalau di jawa, waktu itu hanya mampu menampung 3-4 meja. Namun sekarang telah menjadi besar dengan bangunan baru dan lebih banyak menampung pengunjung. 
Restauran seafood ini menyajikan hidangan ikan laut yang segar, terutama jenis ikan nya (ikan trakulu, bawal, baronang, kakap merah, kerapu..). Kalau kepiting mungkin masih kalah tenar sama Kenari ataupun Dandito, walaupun masakan kepiting saus ataupun lada hitam nya lekeeer juga.
Ukuran ikan cukup mengenyangkan, walau disantap tanpa nasi, cukup dengan sop sayuran pembuka (rasa sop segar dan menggugah selera makan) dan lalapan serta sambal yang terdiri dari beberapa macam (saya sendiri lebih suka sambal bawang dan sambal manga nya buat menemani makan ikan).
Kenyang makan ikan, segelas jeruk peras segar tanpa gula melengkapi makan malam saya (jeruk peras nya asli dari buah dan sangat berasa sekali rasa segarnya).
Bila anda berkunjung ke Balikpapan, sempatkan mampir ke Resturan ini...di jamin puas Harga tidak mahal,  standard restaurant di Balikpapan (1 orang dg menu ikan bakar ukuran besar, nasi, lalap, sambal + minuman tidak sampai Rp. 100 ribu)
Oh ya, lokasi restaurant ini di  JL. Jend. Ahmad Yani, RT. 41 No. 33, Gunung Sari Ilir, 76121, dari arah pertigaan Balikpapan Plaza, masuk jalan Ahmad Yani, sekitar 500 meter sebelah kiri jalan.
Selamat mencoba ya!!
reviews.title: Langganan Makan Seafood di Balikpapan dari th 2005

reviews.text: Penasaran atas saran kawan. Saya ajak kawan-kawan dan kami meluncur ke Teluk Bayur. Setelah duduk dan diberi lembar menu, kami diarahkan ke lemari pendingin untuk memesan berbagai menu hasil laut yang ada. Mulai udang, kepiting, kerang, ikan, cumi-cumi hingga cah kailan. Beberapa minuman kami pesan, dari es jeruk hingga minuman ringan. Setelah memesan bahan dan metode masaknya, kami duduk di meja dengan pandangan yang strategis dan tak lama kemudian satu-persatu makanan dan minuman yang kami pesan datang. Mulai dari minuman yang kami pesan tadi, kerang rebus, cah kailan, kepiting lada hitam, udang bakar, ikan goreng dan disusul menu yang lainnya. Secara garis besar, seafood disini mantap, rasanya segar dan gurih. Udang bakarnya besar namun tidak di belah di bagian punggungnya sebelum dibakar, sehingga masih kurang renyah menurut saya. Secara umum, untuk jamuan makan malam bersama kawan-kawan disini mantap dan enak.
reviews.title: Seafoodnya mantap

name: Bakso dan Mie Pangsit Wardoyo
address: Jl. MT Haryono Dalam, Balikpapan Indonesia

reviews.text:

Finding a parking slot is another story so you'd better go there with taxis or ojek. The bakso and mie ayam is yuuummm Will come back again to this place, for sure!

I often to come here with my friends, the meet ball is delicious.
The area is nice and comfort. The price is cheap and absolutely great place to hang out with your friends

Very tasty , cheap . But a bit hard for searching parking  I recommend you guys use grab  , gojek or uber for going here . 
Their mie ayam also not bad , but i more prefer to eat bakso with mie putih .
reviews.title: Bakso and mee ayam

reviews.text: I am not a fans of bakso (meat ball) and mie ayam (chicken noodle) here in Balikpapan, but when I found this place, I am grateful. They have Solo style, I mean the Mie Ayam has a sweet taste, which I like. The portion is generous, even they give the soy sauced cooked chicken chunks a lot. The best one for me would be the bakso. They serve it with chunks of fat and lot of adhering meats and they are giving you that as much as you asked. The price will you make you happy.
reviews.title: So glad to find this place..

photos.caption: Mie Ayam and Bakso Pangsit... Amazing..

reviews.text: I am not a fan of Bakso but still OK with Mie Ayam. However in Balikpapan, I found none of those foods which are good in my tongue, until I came to this place. Their portion are so generous with nice taste, above averages. Their Bakso is completed with adhering meat and cow fat, my favorites, while the Mie Ayam served with a very good chunks of chicken cooked with sweet soy sauce. All served with generous portion, you may asked more if you want. The place is OK and price is kind of cheap.
reviews.title: Best Bakso and Mie Ayam in Balikpapan so far

Disini selain selalu penuh karena akhir pekan, juga karena sudah malam ketika saya datang. Untuk makan malam saja, saya menjadikan gerai makan ini menjadi pilihan yang enak, berkuah dan hangat.

reviews.title: Local restaurant with great coffee and good breakfast

reviews.text:
Depot ini populer sebagai tempat sarapan di Balikpapan. Konsepnya mirip mini foodcourt di dalam satu ruko. Ada beberapa lemari food display dengan stafnya masing-masing. Ada yang menjual nasi kuning, adayang menjual lontong sayur, ada yang menjual macam-macam kue dan ada yang menjual minuman. Mirip foodcourt versi mini.
Saya mencoba nasi kuning dengan lauk telur dan ayam semur, Kuah ayam semurnya lumayan, nasi kuning agak mengecewakan, rasanya relatif hambar. 
Beruntung kue bintangnya saya sangat suka. Bentuknya mirip pia (bundar, tidak berbentuk bintang, entah mengapa dinamakan bintang) dengan isian kacang hijau, saya suka tekstur kue dan isiannya. 
Makanan lain belum mencoba, karena baru pertama kali datang di rumah makan ini.
reviews.title: Tempat sarapan populer di Balikpapan dengan konsep mirip mini foodcourt

reviews.text:
Pertama kalinya cobain sarapan di Depot Miki. Tempat yang direkomendasikan teman saya kalau ke Balikpapan untuk mampir makan disini.

Depot Miki seperti ruko lama, yang didalamnya terdapat counter macam-macam makanan, ada nasik kuning, mie ayam, lontong sayur, nasi pecel, dll.
Minumannya juga beragam, dari kopi susu, teh susu, teh tarik, dll.

Saya pesan nasi kuning khasnya kalimantan yang dicampur dengan mie, telor dengan saos balado yang rasanya khas banget . 

Harganya terjangkau dan pelayanannya cukup cepat. Kalau mau sarapan disarankan untuk datang lebih awal sekitar jam 8an, saya datang jam 10 sudah tinggal sisa dan pada habis.
reviews.title: Sarapan di Balikpapan

reviews.text: Tempat ini ramai pada pagi menjelang siang hari, konsepnya seperti foodcourt dimana kita bisa memesan sendiri makanan kita di booth yang kita inginkan, yang terkenal adalah nasi kuningnya, tapi menurut saya biasa saja, tapi kelebihannya adalah banyak pilihan makanan yang bisa dipilih, tempatnya juga agak panas
reviews.title: Tempat sarapan wajib balikpapan

reviews.text: Depot ini selalu ramsi saat jam sarapan,mulai buka jam 7 pagi WITA dan tutup jam 3 sore.Dua ksli saya sarapan disini dan selalu penuh pengunjung.Nadi kuningnya juara dan taste berbeda dengan nasi kuning di jawa timur.Bubur ayam menu yang banyak dipesan pengunjung,pusang goreng dan kopi hitam.Ada nadi tim ayam kampung juga.Dijual menu2 lain seperti nadi pecel dan anrka bakpau.
reviews.title: Sarapan pagi nikmat

reviews.text: tempatnya sederhana dan tanpa pendingin udara jadi agak gerah, makanannya lumayan variatif untuk makan siang.
reviews.title: lumayan untuk makan siang

name: Bebek Goreng H. Slamet
address: Jln. Jendral Sudirman 74, Balikpapan 76112 Indonesia

reviews.text:
Although a franchise by nature still the best of all bebek genre retraurants in town.
Probably in the country as well.
I love the suwir / shredded bebek menu. Note to the chef, not too salty please.
Overall, keep the good work!
reviews.title: Still the best

reviews.text:
Only one choice on the menu .... Bebek ( Duck). 
Great taste, you can have it cooked crispy , crunchy or normal. It is served with rice and veges, with a spicy sauce .   You can bu the whole duck or a quarter.     The furniture and deco are very basic but we don't go there for the deco ......
reviews.title: Nice crispy duck

reviews.text: Bebek goreng H.Slamet is my favourite place to eat fried duck. I love fried duck and H.Slamet have the best taste for it. The savory flavor of the duck is really special and their sambal is very addictive
reviews.title: My favourite fried duck

reviews.text: Dangerously delicious and addictive, order the "remuk" version and you'll be blown away.. if you like hot sambal, H. Slamet will deliver.
reviews.title: You've been warned

reviews.text: The taste of the food is nice but the amount is too small. the price is rather expensive. the place is average
reviews.title: Food is nice

reviews.text:
I am not a fan of deep fried food, so when my friends invited me for lunch at Bebek Goreng Slamet I wasn't really excited about it but decided to try it.
For my surprise the bebek goreng remuk is pretty good. Very crispy, prefectly fried without being too oilly. 
Great meal!
reviews.title: Surprisingly good!

reviews.text: One of the most popular fried duck restaurant in Indonesia. They serve the authentic Javanese style fried duck with special chili sauce. You can order the duck to be fried crispy or wet. The taste is very good.
reviews.title: Authentic javanese fried duck

reviews.text: Resto ini tempatnya nyaman dengan layanan yang baik serta memuaskan. Menu andalannya Bebek goreng. Selain itu tersedia juga Ayam goreng. Ayam gorengnya rasanya enak dan gurih dengan daging yang empuk. Sambalnya terasa nikmat dan mantap. Tempe dan tahunya juga enak dan gurih. Setelah itu minum jeruk hangat rasanya segar dan nikmat.
reviews.title: Enak dan Nikmat

reviews.text: Potongan bebek gorengnya cukup besar dengan rasa yang renyah, yang paling mantap adalah sambal matahnya. Suasana rumah makan bersih dan layanan cepat. Sangat direkomendasikan bagi penggemar bebek goreng.
reviews.title: Bebek Goreng dengan sambal yang mantap

reviews.text: Merupakan bagian jaringan rumah makan khas menu bebek, jadi jangan pesan selain menu andalan kecuali ada alergi. Rasanya sangat enak dan pas di lidah, disertai sambal korek yang pedasnya pas sekali untuk lidah Indonesia. Disarankan minum jeruk hangat untuk mengurangi efek pedasnya, hindari minuman dingin apalagi es.
reviews.title: Khas Bebek Solo

reviews.text: Rasa makanan standard bebek slamet. Bebek gurih dan tidak amis. Konsep restoran seperti saung sehingga terasa nyaman
reviews.title: Alternatif Makanan Selain Seafood

reviews.text:
I am not a duck person actually, tapi begitu cobain bebek goreng disini ternyata rasanya enak banget. Bebek tersedia dalam beberapa tipe, ada utuh dan remuk (garing-garing gitu). dan sambelnya itu sambel korek, that is the best part!

bebek nya gurih banget rasaanyaaa!! ditambah sambel korek. well what can i say, super yummy!!

xx
reviews.title: The best!

reviews.text: Restaurant ini memiliki beberapa gerai yang sudah tersebar di berbagai kota besar di Indonesia, salah satuya di Balikapan. Makan siang disini bersama rekan kerja, mencoba mencicipi bebeknya yang sudah terkenal kelezatannya. Rasa bebeknya mantap, gurih dan krispi, sambalnya juga mantap, harganya wajar.
reviews.title: Makan Siang, Bebeknya Lezat

reviews.text: Sengaja makan siang disini untuk perbandingan dengan outlet di pulau Jawa. Setelah masuk, saya dicegat langsung di meja pembayaran untuk memesan, tanpa banyak kata, saya memilih bebek goreng bagian paha dan es teh. Hendak memilih dada bebek ternyata sudah habis. Setelah memesan, saya kemudian duduk dak tak lama kemudian es teh datang. Selang lima belas menit kemudian pesana saya datang. Untuk sambalnya saya merasakan masih bisa pedas lagi. Menurut saya, ukuran bebeknya bisa lebih besar lagi, namun karena ini cabang yang relatif jauh dari pusatnya,  saya bisa memaklumi. Untuk ukuran making siang saya rasa cukup.
reviews.title: Bebeknya bisa lebih besar lagi

reviews.text:
Ga pernah bosen, walaupun menu nya cuman bebek goreng. Favorit andalan berdua ama suami. Klo ga makan siang yach makan malem. Ajak keluarga juga asyiikkk. Tempatnya nyatai bisa lesehan dan leyeh-leyeh...

Sukakkk
reviews.title: Late dinner

reviews.text: Ayam,bebek,goreng maupun bakarnya semua ue....nak.buka dimana mana.sambalnya ada 6 sampai 8 macam.bisa pilih,bisa ambil sesukanya.lalapannya juga mau ambil satu piring penuh?boleh coy ....sesukanya deh
reviews.title: Sambalnya........macam2

reviews.text:
Siapa yang nggak tau resto Bebek H slamet ini, cita rasa dari tahun 1986 yang berpusat di kartosuro, solo.
Menu utama disini memang cuma bebek goreng (tidak ada olahan lain seperti bebek bakar, dll) namun bukan cuma bebek goreng biasa.
Menurut saya rasa bebek goreng H slamet memang sangat enak, bumbu rempahnya sangat terasa dan tekstur daging bebeknya pun sangat lembut. Di tambah lagi dengan sambal korek yang super pedas, dijamin bakal menambah selera makan.
Harga bebek slamet ini cukup tidak membuat kantong jebol harga 1 ekor tidak sampai 100,000 dan jika menginginkan paket bisa membeli pake paha/dada hanya 30,000 an dada/paha + nasi + sambal dan tempe mendoan (belum termasuk minum).
Untuk pelayan disini juga cukup cepat tanpa menunggu lama makanan yang di pesan akan segera di sajikan dalam keadaan masih panas.
reviews.title: Bebek goreng yang bener-bener mak yos

reviews.text: Enak untuk makan sekeluarga, bebeknya empuk dan sambalnya ok banget.... cocok buat yang suka pedas.....
reviews.title: Makan Keluarga

reviews.text:
Biasanya makan di sini kala dalam kondisi lapar, dan memesan 1 ekor bebek utuh, karena rasanya lezat sekali, dan sambalnya khusus.
Sebaiknya makan ditempat dan jangan dibungkus karena rasanya akan berbeda....
reviews.title: Rasa Bebek yang tidak terlupakan

reviews.text: Bebek goreng remuk dan sambal koreknya yang selalu saya pesen klo kesini. Untuk sambalnya saya bisa nambah 2 atau 3 porsi lagi walopun ini ga free lohh hahah. Sebenernya tingkat pedes sambalnya sih ampun-ampun tapi bikin nagih. Oiya disini ada resoules isi mayonise, daging asap atau keju yang bisa dibungkus untuk cemilan dibawa pulang.
reviews.title: Bebek Kriuk !!

name: RM Bunaken Indah
address: Jln. Jendral Sudirman 245, Balikpapan 76112 Indonesia

reviews.text:
Many selections here. A la carte, buffet style presentation. Some meals are rotate weekly based. You can dine in and buy as 
"nasi bungkus". But beware if you buy meal per portion as it is huge in amount and in price! Try order to go half portion first and see the amount and price as suit you.
Special dishes recommended : sayur jantung pisang ( banana bud ) & sayur daun pakis ( fiddleheads ). 
Most dishes are spicy. Overall it's highly recommended for both people seldom tasting Manado's food or have craving for in Balikpapan. happy tasting
reviews.title: Complete menu & good taste overall

reviews.text: The menus are completed and the taste remind me of Manado and its story. The price is cheap. Location good.  But please pay attention in cleanliness of the food, hopefully no flies fly arround on the rica-ricas and wokus
reviews.title: The Authentic Menu of Kawanua in Balikpapan

reviews.text: Resto ini tempatnya nyaman dengan layanan yang ramah dan baik. Menu cukup beragam. Ayam goreng mentega rasanya enak. Ayamnya  dibentuk fillet tepung dengan irisan tipis serta digoreng dengan mentega. Disajikan dengan senangkuk kecil saus nanas rasanya manis asam. Ikan bakar rasanya enak dengan bumbu yang meresap serta daging yang lembut. Sayur jantung pisang rasanya enak dan mantap.
reviews.title: Masakan Enak

reviews.text: bagi pencinta kuliner, wajib untuk datang ke RM Bunaken Indah, menyajikan banyak sekali varian menu yang enak dan lezat
reviews.title: kuliner

reviews.text: Makanan manado paling enak se-Balikpapan.. ada 2 cabang.. di jendral sudirman n balikpapan baru.. yang di balikpapan baru skarang ada menu malamnya loh dari am 6-11 malam... ada ba tore n ba putar... yummyy...
reviews.title: Makanan manado terenak se-Balikpapan

reviews.text: Salah satu rumah makan Menado di Balikpapan. Lokasi yang di Jend. sudirman sangat strategis. Rasa masakan cukup enak. Pilih hidangan laut sebagai makanan favorit.
reviews.title: RM Menado

reviews.text: Terdapat 2 cabang RM Bunaken Indah di Balikpapan, satu di Jl. Sudirman dan satu lagi di Komplek Balikpapan Baru. Menu yang wajib dicoba adalah Nasi Kuning Manado, Mie Cakalang, dan Es Kacang Merah dengan Gula Merah.
reviews.title: Rumah Makan Manado Paling Enak di Balikpapan

reviews.text: RM Bunaken Indah menjual berbagai makan khas manado oleh karena itu hampir semua makanannya merupakan makanan khas manado, baik itu makanan besar ataupun makanan kecilnya. Rasanyapun cukup enak-enak.
reviews.title: Rumah makan kas manado yang sangat enak.

reviews.text: saat berkunjung ke kota Balikpapan dan pengen ngerasain seafood yg yummi... RM Bunaken Indah bisa jd tempat makan yg cocok looh....
reviews.title: mau hidangan laut, di mari jg lumayan

reviews.text: RM Bunaken Indah menyajikan makanan ala Minahasa / Manado yang terkenal dengan tingkat kepedasannya. Tidak lengkap sebuah rumah makan Minahasa tanpa sambal / rica / dabu-dabu. Rumah makan ini menyediakan makanan prasmanan.
reviews.title: Rumah makan Minahasa di Balikpapan

reviews.text:
Jenis makanan cukup lengkap. Kebetulan pas hari ini ada menu RW. Beberapa macam ikan bakar, cumi hitam dan bisa juga memesan B2 dalam bebrrapa menu.
Bubur manado dan mie cakalang juga tersedia.
Kue2 sanggat mengoda.
Tempat makan cukip luas dan pelayanan cepat. 
Model makan prasmanan. 
1 piring sekitar 20 ribu bila ditambah menu lain beda harga.
Rasa enak dan harga masih masuk akal.
reviews.title: Salah satu rumah makan manado di Balikpapan

reviews.text: Kangen dengan makanan Manado saat bertugas di Balikpapan ? Tidak terlalu susah mencarinya, salah satu yang saya rekomendasikan adalah RM Bunaken Indah, letaknya di tengah kota dan makanannya lezat serta layanannya baik dan cepat.
reviews.title: Salah satu resto Manado terbaik di Balikpapan

name: Restaurant Sea Food Apong
address: Jl. Marsma R. Iswahyudi Gunung Bakaran no. 124 blok A-2, Balikpapan Indonesia

reviews.text: Can't stop thinking about its yummy sup asparagus, very recommended. Also kepiting angsio with its special sauce.
reviews.title: Recommended restaurant

reviews.text:
This (not so) new (anymore) place is very clean and have lots of choices. We usually order kerang saus padang, kangkung asap (very delicious), ikan kudu-kudu masak telur asin. Overall is good. 
There's only one thing that i don't like from this restaurant is that they hide their scale behind the counter. It just doesn't seem right.
reviews.title: Im here for their Kerang Saus Padang

reviews.text: A new place opened to add option for seafood haven in Balikpapan. The tastes here for me was good, above average. The place itself properly designed, fresh. They have signature dish which is "kepiting termos" meaning sauced crab in a jar. Creative. Price is fair for such place.
reviews.title: New seafood haven

reviews.text:
We were having our lunch together with our business partners from Malaysia and Australia. We ordered udang saus padang, soup asam ikan kerapu , cumi goreng tepung, kangkung cah and kepiting masak Angsio. 

All seafood so fresh and yummy, especially udang saus padang and kepiting angsio.... Fully recommended for seafood lovers...
reviews.title: Udang Saus Padang so yummy...

reviews.text: Having an iftar dinner with colleagues, and eat so many delicious food. The crab was awesome, vegetable was average, sate ayam was also great, the fish and squid were good and yummy.
reviews.title: Good for iftar dinner

reviews.text: Apong serves very good and fresh seafood. We ordered grilled fish, fried fish, fish soup, steamed clam and vegetable dishes. All were delicious. The service was good. They also have separate room you could reserve for family function or business meeting.
reviews.title: Good Food Nice Restaurant

reviews.text: Wow! This place offers great and fresh seafood. So delicious and yummy! Clean and nice place to dine with friends and business associates. The signature dish of spicy crabs was so good that you wanna come back here for more. Highly recommended to try out this restaurant seafood.
reviews.title: Fresh n Great Seafood

reviews.text: Salah satu destinasi restoran seafood favorit di kota Balikpapan. Menu seafoodnya sangat enak, didepan bisa memilih dahulu ikan2 yang akan dipesan. Suasana dalam restoran juga sangat bagus dan ada ruangan khusus VIP atau private jika ingin makan bareng keluarga atau kolega. Menu favorit kami disini yaitu ikan kudu-kudu telur asin..rasanya enak dan gurih. Kalau mau  pesan kepiting dan dibawa pulang juga tersedia direstoran ini. Pokoknya keren dan recommended.
reviews.title: Mantappp...Enak dan Kerenn...

reviews.text: Makan siang disini. Menu ikan laut. Enak enak... otak otak tengirinya enak. Ca kangkung spesial hot plate nya recomended.
reviews.title: Makanan enak

reviews.text:
Tidak sabar menu ikan kudu-kudu telur asin, ketika akhirnya datang 2 ekor, langsung habis disantap 4 orang.
Menu ikan bakarnya juga kumplit, tinggal pilih yang disuka langsung bakar.
Sayurnya kupilih taoge ikan asin.
Terakhir udang besar, hanya muat sebuah saja.
reviews.title: Kudu-kudu telur asin

reviews.text: Resto ini tempatnya nyaman dengan penataan yang baik dan serasi. Layanannya ramah serta memuaskan. Tersedia menu seperti Sup ikan, Cumi goreng, Ikan bakar, Ca kangkung, Ikan goreng, Otak-otak, Kepiting asap dan sebagainya. Sup ikan rasanya segar dan nikmat. Ca kangkung rasanya nikmat dan mantap. Ikan goreng rasanya gurih dan nikmat dengan daging yang lembut.
reviews.title: Seafood Nikmat

reviews.text: Ini termasuk resto seafood yang direkomendasikan klien saya,Ikan kudu-kudu masak telur asinnya enak dan dilengkapi dengan 3 macam sandal dan ada lalap tomat hijau.Sambal taoconya enak banget.Must try deh
reviews.title: Ikan Kudu-Kudunya harus dicoba

reviews.text: pilihan menu saya disini adalah kepiting saus padang, kepiting lada hitam, ikan papare dan bumbu rica, cumi goreng mentega dan kangkung cah. semuanya enak dan mantap rasanya. kangkung cah hotplate dicampur dengan udang dan telur burung. enak banget. ga salah pilihan saya untuk lunch
reviews.title: yummy

reviews.text: Restoran ini menu andalannya adalah makanan laut. Pertama kali melangkahkan kaki ke dalam, langsung disambut waitress nya. Duduk dan pesan. Di sinilah masalah berawal, saat melihat menu, tidak ada satupun harga tertera termasuk minumannya. Saya bertanya kepada waitress kenapa tidak ada daftar harganya, hal ini disebabkan harga sesuai berat dari ikan, atau kepiting. Mereka tidak memberlakukan harga per porsi. Ayolah, bahkan untuk minuman pun tidak ada harganya? Apakah harus ditimbang juga minumannya? Di restoran lain sejenis mereka ada daftar harga. Apabila memang sulit karena harus ditimbang, buatlah harga per 100 gram nya. It's not that hard to be fair to your customer. Menurut saya, gaya restoran seperti ini tidak dapat ditoleransi. Dengan menjamurnya restoran seafood sejenis, serta rasa masakan di restoran ini yang tidak terlalu berbeda dengan restoran lainnya, tidak akan menunggu waktu lama untuk ditinggalkan oleh pelanggan. Saran saya, play it fair, jangan terlalu terobsesi dengan keuntungan yang hendak diraup. Dan, harga di restoran ini memang outrage. No need to eat in this restaurant unless they treat you right and fair, which they don't.
reviews.title: Tidak ada daftar harga di menunya

reviews.text: Kalo ke Balikpapan kebetulan lagi menjemput orang di bandara atau lagi jalan-jalan jangan lupa mampir ke restorant satu ini. Letaknya cukup dekat Dr bandara. Tempat makannya bersih, seafoodnya cukup lengkap and yang paling penting delicious. Yang paling saya suka disini otak-otak ikannya, oh iya cobai juga kangkung asap mereka dari penampilan sudah menggoda apalg rasanya
reviews.title: Seafood mantap

reviews.text: Ada menu baru ternyata kepiting Asap apong mantap lain dari yang lain sama kepiting karinya yummmy harga sesuai rasa
reviews.title: Good service

reviews.text: makanan enak dan cukup murah hanya parkiran untuk kendaraan kurang.. Recommended seafood restaurant.
reviews.title: Makanan Enak dan harga cukup murah

reviews.text:
Jika Anda rindu untuk makan seafood dengan rasa ala Makassar, tidak salah jika Anda memilih Restoran Apong.

Restoran ini menyediakan berbagai jenis ikan yang berbeda dari restoran lainnya dan juga rasanya yang sangat menggoda lidah Anda

Tempatnya luas dan nyaman untuk santap di tempat
reviews.title: Restoran Sea Food One of The Best di Balikpapan

reviews.text: Mengulang kesuksesannya di Makasar dan sekaligus menjadi salah satu pilihan oleh-oleh terbaru yang dapat kita beli di restoran ini untuk kita bawa pulang sebagai oleh-oleh, yaitu "Kepiting Termos".
reviews.title: Kepiting Termos

reviews.text:
Sebenarnya ada restoran   kepiting lain yang sudah lebih lama terkenal di Balikpapan, namun teman saya di Balikpapan mengajak mencoba Restoran yang lebih baru dan lebih fresh ini.
Ternyata begitu mencoba makanannya wah...lebih mak nyuss dibanding restoran jenis sama yang sering menjadi destinasi saya di Balikpapan
reviews.title: Menikmati Makanan laut dan Kepiting Lezat

name: XO Suki & Dim Sum
address: Jln. Jendral Sudirman Balikpapan Super Block Blok G 10 - 11, Balikpapan 76112 Indonesia

reviews.text:
the food itself quite pricey, you can find more delicious suki at Balikpapan with cheaper price.
The restaurant is comfortable and good for family or groups.
reviews.title: so so..

reviews.text: Chinese cuisine and dim sum menu indulgent tongue, and also suki fresh menu, perfect for a meal with family or spouse or coworkers
reviews.title: BEST CHINESE CUISINE & DIMSUM

reviews.text: By staying in Grand Jatra hotel, I guess this resto was good option rather than went to the mall for lunch or dinner. Variety of suki was a pro for this resto although when we ordered drinks for the second time, it took forever to wait.
reviews.title: Good option if you stay at Grand Jatra

reviews.text: It's located in E-Walk mall Balikpapan. Lots of variety in suki, delicious tom yam and chicken broth for suki..... other variety of foods also delicious. Like the coconut pudding as well !!
reviews.title: Delicious Suki in Balikpapan

reviews.text:
Juz now, me and colleagues were having dinner together after meeting.
Like every other suki resto, they served kind of food for suki. I took caisim for the vedgie options bcoz thas the only veggie there that looked fresh. There were only 3 kind of vedgie,

When we had the suki ready, the taste of the soup (both tomyam and chicken) was really yummy that made me add some more bowls.

But something really made me lose my appetite. I found a small green caterpillar in my soup!!!!!!
Something that we can found in vedgetables that had not been cleaned!!

Really lose my appetite!
We showed it to the supervisor in charge there, and he looked shocked, but said nothing to us.

The main point for a resto that even u have bad service u must have a clean food for customer.

Clean food is a MUST!
reviews.title: Clean food is a MUST :(

reviews.text: i do love suki. wherever in this part of the worlf i'm always looking for suki. my favorite in xo suki is baso salmon and bakpao.
reviews.title: Suki seeker

reviews.text: Its good to see balik has a great place like this to eat. By far the best meal we have had since we have been here. I highly recommend.
reviews.title: Best meal for this trip by far

reviews.text:
Like any other suki restaurant, you can choose which food you would like to have in your soup.
The tom yum soup is very good, I don't usually eat tom yum, but I do here. Options are quite many, I think it's on par to other good suki restaurant. Service was good and atmosphere was also very good. I went here during a business trip for lunch and it's a nice change to all the seafood I usually have in the area.
reviews.title: Fancy Suki

reviews.text: The food is decent but slightly overpriced for what we paid. And it also lack of variety for the suki tray compared to other places that I visited before. The only good thing is the location where can easily be found in BSB mall.
reviews.title: A little overpriced!

reviews.text:
I went with my Girlfriend because she wanted to try it, having heard about it from friends.

Before going I had read reviews on TripAdvisor saying the Suki was overpriced, so decided to avoid that.

We arrived late lunch on Sunday, with about 65% of the tables being empty, most of which were dirty.

They guided us to a table near the front of the restaurant and we sat down.

The waitress brought us menus and stood waiting to take our order.
This is something I have noticed all over Indonesia, the waiting staff are never trained to plan time and service correctly (take a drinks order, bring back the drinks, allow the customers to study the menu, then take the order) however it could be because the Indonesian people (usually the women) never read the menu and always ask the waiting staff what they have.

The waitress gave us our drinks and went away, leaving us to study the menu.

The menu was disappointing.

It is a standard restaurant chain menu, thicker pages for strength and easily wiped to keep it clean (unfortunately both menus felt a little sticky and dirty).

The variety is OK (if it was all available), but it is noticable that the majority of items offered are factory made items, take from a box and cook (you can cook them in your own home for less).

The menu had hand written stickers, almost on every page, saying Sold Out, as an estimation, 30-40%.
In one area, of the two pages facing each other, only 20% of the products were available; this is very poor management by the company, seeing as most of the food is factory made; if it is not, the standard was very disappointing.
This scenario is not due to a busy lunchtime service, but a long term failure.

We ordered:

Siomay
Prawn Roll Fried
Small Bread Roll with Chicken inside
Beef with Black Pepper
 Roast Duck
Brocolli with Garlic
White Rice
1 beer and 1 fruit juice

The rice was brought to the table within 10 minutes of being ordered and we thought the food would arrive soon; how wrong we were.   After a further 15 minutes we asked where our food was, 10 minutes later the food started to arrive, we had to ask for the rice to be replaced, so we had hot rice to eat with the other dishes.

As has previously been reported, the duck was good.

The brocolli was nice and it was cooked properly, a little firm to the tooth.

The black pepper beef was disappointing, in fact bland, it was in a factory style black pepper sauce that had little flavour and no spice that could be tasted.

The rest of the food was average and edible.

As for the Suki, we could see the refrigerators with all the opened containers of Suki in them; open to the elements and peoples fingers and sneezing.

We observed several people visit and take containers after picking others up, sometimes holding them close to their noses and sniffing them.

This was not the worst thing we saw, many children were visiting the refrigerators with their guardians and their fingers were prodding the food, we saw one lick some food and put it back.   We all know childrens fingers regularly go down the front and back of their pants as well as up their noses and in their mouths, without being washed.

The staff were courtious, but a little disorganised.

When the bill came we were unpleasantly surprised how expensive it was, it was no cheaper than going to Oceans Restaurant, considered one of the more expensive restaurants in Balikpapan and despite some of the doubtful management I have experienced there (see other reviews), I would say the cooking is far superior, mainly because it is prepared and cooked on site.

If you want Asian fast food similar to this I would suggest looking elsewhere in Balikpapan, perhaps go to Tah Wan in Balikpapan Plaza, where the food is similar, but much cheaper and quicker.

I am sorry to say I will not return to this restaurant again.
reviews.title: Over priced and under quality

name: Mandarin Chinese Restaurant
address: Bandar Balikpapan Ruko  Jln. Jendral Sudirman, Balikpapan 76112 Indonesia

reviews.text:
Mandarin Chinese Restaurant is found in the Ruko area of Klandasan, on the street side of the Rukos that house Ocean's, Zeus and Connexions.

Mandarin operates Lunch and Dinner times; in the evening 18:00 to 22:00.

Mandarin says it is halal, however, it depends upon your interpretation of halal; for many Sunni Muslim people from the Middle East, it is not Halal.

We went there at around 18:30, we were the first in the restaurant.
There were clear defined eating areas; tables of up to 4 with no tablecloth, round tables up to 8 diners with tablecloths and larger rectangular tables of 10 - 14 people with no tablecloths (there was also a private dining room with several round dining tables and special entertainment systems).

We had fish lips soup, Fried Rice Yang Chow (completely different to Ocean's version, both are variations on the original recipe, but Ocean's is closer), Spinach with shrimps and quails eggs (the quails eggs were not as good quality as the ones I have had delivered to rigs in the area or bought in Hero Balikpapan Baru, the yolks were not as creamy, in fact, more watery and slightly metalic in taste.), Satay Seafood (sizzling), Beef in Black Pepper, Roast Duck and Hainan Rice, washed down with Jasmine Tea.

The ambiance was not so good with TV, background music and Karaoke in the private room; at the same time; later there would be a singer and backing group.

The service of the staff was attentive, but not intrusive, they have clearly been trained well.

Sadly (due to its location) Mandarin does not have the atmosphere of Ocean's, but, it has food to match and service too, at a slightly cheaper price. 

I will return.
reviews.title: A good restaurant, with food and service to enjoy

reviews.text: A very nice place to have Chinese food in Balikpapan. A fancy restaurant. They serve great chinese food. I love the mustard sauced shrimp and fried chicken the most. The place is quiet, perfect place to dine with spouse or closed friend. The price is normal for such place.

reviews.text:
Tahun lalu bertepatan dengan ulang tahun om saya, saya ingin mengajak dia ke sebuah restoran untuk merayakannya. Kebetulan tempat ini belum pernah kami kunjungi. Sebenarnya agak ragu masuk, karena takut makanannya tidak sesuai di lidah. Semoga tampilan mewah restorannya sesuai dengan rasanya. 
Sampai di dalam ruangan yg terlihat mewah, bersih, dan rapi kita langsung diarahkan di meja yang tersedia sesuai jumlah anggota keluarga. Suasanya chinesenya begitu kental, diiringi musik jazz yg dimainkan seorang artist dari pojok ruangan. Karena sudah lapar, jadi kita langsung memesan makanan dan tidak pakai lama makanan pun satu persatu datang. Ketika mencicipi satu persatu makanannya, wow!! sangat lezat, ternyata tidak rugi kita memilih tempat ini. Memang harganya lumayan, tetapi standard lah untuk restoran china. Untuk makanan recommanded sepertinya semuanya deh, karena memang enak semua. Saya tulis review ini lagi jadi pengen kesana lagi hehe.

reviews.text: Resto ini mudah dijumpai karena terletak di jalan utama yang dilalui angkutan umum. Tempatnya cukup luas dan bersih, nyaman untuk makan bersama keluarga. Masakan terkenal enak dan memang enak tapi porsinya tidak sebanding dengan harganya. Pelayanan bagus tapi harus menunggu cukup lama dari memesan sampai makanan disajikan. Masakan ayam entah dimasak bumbu apa saja satu porsi Rp 80.000 tp porsinya hanya cukup untuk 2-3 orang. Kalau mau makan di sini yah persiapkan minimal Rp 100rb/orang.

Restaurant provide a big screen display in order to show some live event such a football or Motogp and other live show.
reviews.title: Great Palumara soup

reviews.text:
Initially I had planned to go to Ocean's restaurant next door with my girlfriend, but it was so busy, I knew the service would not be good and we would be upset.

We turned round and walked away, but my girlfriend wanted to eat in this area, so we decided to try Zeus.

We were greeted by courteous staff and shown to a table.
There were several tables, with around 40 to 50 people eating at the restaurant.

We initially sat by the sea, but the wind was a little too strong for my girlfriend, so we moved to a table near the main building.

We studied the menu; it was much less varied than the Ocean's menu, but had all the key things anyone would want.

We had a whole grilled grouper, chicken with peanut sauce, beef with black pepper, soup, vegetables, rice, 2 large Bintang beer and a fresh fruit juice.

The food is good, with lots of flavour and nice to eat.

The service was good, with all the food arriving within 10 minutes of the first dish.

The portions are smaller than Ocean's, but still enough for  you to have a good meal; this difference is reflected in the price.

We enjoyed our meal, ate all the food and did not want any more to eat, it was a perfectly calculated meal and showed that the manager and chef knew exactly what they were doing.

After consuming all this food and drink, we received a bill of only Rp288,000, on top of this we received a further 15% discount because my girlfriend used her Mandiri card.

It was a good meal, I will return and recommend it to other people.
reviews.title: A pleasant surprise

reviews.text:
Need to have strong and healthy body to have dinner by the beach as the wind was too heavy at this place. Food is good and the price is not expensive, live music is there although sometimes the sound is beaten by the wave sound....
Overall still recommended

reviews.text: Restoran ini letaknya di pusat kota dan persis di tepi laut. Harganya relatif terjangkau dan pemandangan lautnya juga ok. Pilihan menunya juga cukup beragam.
reviews.title: Restoran tepi laut

reviews.text: O lugar tinha tudo pra ser bom: tima localizao, confortvel  e de frente para o mar. Mas ao chegar, eu e minha esposa tivemos que mudar de mesa pois comeava a chover. Logo, pedimos uns drinks e entradas, mas depois de quase 10 minutos de haver pedido os aperitivos, o garom nos informou que no estava disponvel. Tentei ver se ele poderia sugerir outra coisa, mas pelo jeito ele era novo no local e no conhecia muito bem o menu. Preferimos nao arriscar e pedimos o clssico spaguetti Quando chegou, j estava meio frio o prato e o molho bem ruinzinho. Minha esposa achou que o prato dela estava muito picante e ofereceram um molho adocicado para "quebrar um pouco a pimenta". No fim, o macarro ficou horrvel e no conseguimos terminar de jantar. Tentei falar com o encarregado pra ver se rolava um desconto, mas no havia ningum disponvel no momento. Samos de l desapontados pelo custo-benefcio do local.
reviews.title: Jantar romntico com pouco romantismo

It is definitely one of the best sea food resto in Balikpapan.
Fresh bawal bakar, superb sambal, and also coconut.

reviews.text: Aroma ikan bakar disini enak banget dan ternyata rasanya juga memang enak, tempatnya standar dan bersih.

Terong bakar rasanya lembut dan nikmat. Sambalnya merupakan sambal tomat yang tidak begitu pedas. Selain itu dilengkapi dengan sayur bayam bening, timun, kemangi serta daun singkong rebus.

reviews.text: Ikan bakar dengan style Makasar (bumbu kuning). Meskipun harganya relative agak mahal, tp yang paling top adalah udang galahnya. Worth the price!!
reviews.title: Ikan bakar Makasar

name: Sky Grill Restaurant
address: Jln. H ARS. Muhammad 7 Gran Senyiur Hotel, 7th Floor, Balikpapan 76112 Indonesia

reviews.text: Like all restos or bars that have "Sky" in front of their names, this resto offers a fancy dining experience with excellent views of Balikpapan city. The food were nice (standard hotel prices) but the service could have been better (to make it a more classy experience). I personnaly had dinner here for my 1st anniversary wedding and made reservations beforehand. Wished they could have gave a little more service like decorations on the table or a slice of a cake, but I realized you have to be specific with these requests and don't expect a surpirse lol.
reviews.title: Fancy Dining with Excellent View

reviews.text:
Picture the following:
You sit in Sky Grill restaurant, enjoy the view and you look forward to having a great meal. 
But you hear the life band playing in the Sky Bar and the music coming from speakers in Sky Restaurant - both approximately in the same strength. After 10 minutes you think you get nuts. You ask the waiter but they consider such a collision as okay. 
After another 10 minutes you just hope that meal is served soon, so that you can be out right after.
I cannot even remember if the food was good. It is impossible to enjoy a decent dinner when sitting in such a noise backdrop.
reviews.title: A recommended venue for deaf people

reviews.text: I have had a lot of meals from this hotel and i absolutely love their sea food preparations ... Its fun going to the sea food counter and choosing what you want to eat ... Their Black Pepper crab is absolutely delicious ... Its a rooftop restaurant with ample seating and the tables are nicely spaced out as well ... A nice place for a romantic dinner or a family dinner as well ... Its just below the Sky Bar so you can enjoy a few drinks before heading for dinner
reviews.title: Excellent food and excellent service

reviews.text:
People of Balikpapan and visitors to Gran Senyiur hotel know of the Sky Grill on the 7th floor (just below the Sky Bar), but not many know of the ability to eat Teppanyaki there.

Rather than sit in the Japanese restaurant, you can eat Teppanyaki (cooked by their Japanese Restaurant Chef) with a good view over Balikpapan.

The food is freshly cooked in front of you, following traditional Japanese ways of cooking and eating.

The quality of the meat and fish used is high and the steak melted in my mouth.

It is worth a try, but it is expensive for Balikpapan (as should be expected).

If you want to make an evening of it, you can have an aperitif in the Sky Bar followed by dinner in the Sky Grill.
reviews.title: Japanese Teppanyaki available, upstairs with an excellent view of Balikpapan

reviews.text: salah satu tempat yang oke buat makan malam dan jika sedang ingin barbeque, sepuasnya dan menunya macam macam.
reviews.title: barbeque sepuasnya

reviews.text: menikmati makan malam disini sempurna banget, bisa melihat pemandangan kota balikpapan sambil menyantap aneka hidangan yang lezat.

reviews.text:
Halal: By Restaurant

Untuk menu makanan disini, dinyatakan halal hanya oleh restauran. Namun tidak ada label Halal MUI.

Strong: 
- Seafoodnya enak, segar, karena kita bisa memilih sendiri ikannya dan bisa melihat langsung proses memasaknya karena menampilkan open kitchen.

- Dapat melihat keindahan Kota Balikpapan dari ketinggian. Karena letak restaurannya yang berada di rooftop.

Weekness: 
- Tidak ada lebel halal.
- Disini menjual juga minuman alkohol, jadi membuat restoran ini tidak akan mendapatkan label halal resmi MUI.
reviews.title: (Halal by Restaurant) Restoran terbaik dengan pemandangan terbaik

reviews.text: Tiap kali makan disini pasti mlm.. krn sambil makan bisa liat view city balikpapan dgn lampu2 yg indah... krn letakx di lt.7... aksesx juga bgs lift sendiri gak nyampur di hotel... so meskipun gak nginep disitu gak perlu hrs masuk kedlm lobby.. buat meeting tempatx disini bisa sambil ngeloby..
reviews.title: Cozy Place for Dinner

reviews.text: Setelah menikmati minuman di Sky Bar, kita bisa melanjutkan makan malam di retoran ini. Terletak satu lantai di bawah Sky Bar, restoran Sky Grill menawarkan aneka jenis masakan, mulai dari masakan sea food, Jepang maupun Eropa.
reviews.title: Makan malam dengan pemandangan kota Balikpapan

name: Iga Bakar Mas Giri
address: Jl. Jendral Sudirman no. 285 Markoni, Balikpapan 76113 Indonesia

reviews.text: This rib restaurant located in central balikpapan precisely in sudirman street. The place sell grill rib and also spicy rib. It is complimented with fried tofu. The portion is big enough for 1 person. The taste is good and the ribs didnt really have any competition from other restaurant in balikpapan.
reviews.title: Delicious rib in town

reviews.text:
Just had a hectic day and marathon meetings with clients. This place is the nearest place to go for short lunch break. 
I order 1 grilled ribs and fresh squize orange. 

Not that long...all the dish is ready, grilled ribs ( but in small size cut) a small bowl of beef-stock, rice and simple green salad. 

I rated this ribs is just flat...still hard and less tender, its just because they use the local one ? Or they can't process it as properly ? For me ....I suggesting to use high-pressure cooker pot, to make those ribs more soft & tender as well as tastier than before.....just because all the seasoning & herbs are cooking together in one.
reviews.title: Last minutes choice..!

reviews.text: I rarely come to here bacuse the service is take to long and when you really hungry, it's just a disaster for you. If you want to eat in here, don't go near the lunch time because it will really crowded and the service will take more longer. But the taste is quite delicious
reviews.title: Long service but great taste

reviews.text:
A couple time back in this city and at last, visited this restaurant and the taste was so delicious.

I was ordering Black pepper one...
reviews.title: Delicious Rib barbeque

reviews.text: Grilled ribs spice was delicious, but i recommend they serve the tendon and meat separately like warung iga leko or teko so people who doesnt want tendon in meat can choose... I try nasi goreng iga too and it was delicious... Cleanliness need to improve and service, please tell the waitress to be more polite :)
reviews.title: You can try...

reviews.text:
I've been here for several times.
The price is standard in Balikpapan, but they give fresh iga so it's worthed.
The place has no AC sobut they have quite open space so it's not hot there.
But I always like the service in here, it takes short time between order and the food comes, it's really short.
They also still open when other restaurant has close like at 10 pm, and everything they serve still fine.
What I love the most in here is the Nasi Goreng Iga. It has good taste for them who love Indonesian food.
The parking area is not really big for car but since I go there by motorcycle it has no problem with me.
reviews.title: Fast serving restaurant with good taste

reviews.text: Clearly stated, they specialized their self in grilled ribs. Lot of choice you can find on the list, however the taste is not special. The price is normal for Balikpapan. A nice place to have your meal.
reviews.title: Grilled rib place

reviews.text:
The ribs was good. Delicious. 
But the parking lot is complicated. And the restaurant environment could be better.
reviews.title: Good food

reviews.text:
If you love Iga bakar, sop buntut, satay, curry tongseng and their derivatives... And love to pig out till you can't hardly breathe without hurting your wallet, you can't go wrong with this one.  Portions are small in comparison to what we used to in Oz...Not a bad thing in this case so that one can order more varieties of dishes. Found this place few years ago when they just opened and became our pig out (once per visit) pilgrimage when visiting Balikpapan.

The venue itself was ordinary with no air conditioning, so you'd sweat like no tomorrow with the tropical weather near equator and hot chili! Wonderful experience with "might" have severe consequences for Chad the next day if you got a bit carried out with the chili.
reviews.title: Smashed Some Iga Bakar with a Mate Piggy!

photos.caption: Iga Bakar Mas Giri in Balikpapan

reviews.text: Soup iga rasanya segar dan nikmat. Sate ayam rasanya enak dengan bumbu yang nikmat serta daging yang empuk. Ayam kampung bakar rasanya enak dan gurih serta dagingnya empuk.
reviews.title: Makan dengan Santai

reviews.text: Kleine porties, goed van smaak en nogal prijzig. Echt smerig te moeten eten in een restaurant waar om je heen fiks gerookt wordt. Kan er geen rookvrij gedeelte komen?
reviews.title: Niet rookvrij

reviews.text: Tempat makan ini cukup nyaman hanya layanannya kurang memuaskan. Tersedia menu seperti Iga goreng tepung asam manis, Sop buntut, Nasi goreng iga, Ca kangkung, Gurame bakar, Gurame goreng, Ca brokoli, Kentang goreng dan sebagainya. Sop buntut rasanya segar dan nikmat. Iga goreng tepung asam manis rasanya nikmat dengan daging yang empuk. Gurame bakar rasanya nikmat dengan daging yang lembut.
reviews.title: Masakan Nikmat

reviews.text:
Terletak di pinggir jalan, dg menu mayoritas grill. Restoran pertama yg kami datangi di balikpapan, tapi seorang pelayan resto melayani kami dg sangat tidak sabaran dan agak ketus ketika kami tanya ttg menu yg tersedia. Akhirnya kami memilih iga bakar dan kentang goreng. Lagi2 makanan diletakkan di meja kami dg agak kasar. Sungguh menyedihkan. 
Kentang goreng yg datang ternyata juga mengagetkan. Kentang agak kehitaman, keras dg rasa belum matang. Kami hanya makan beberapa. Iga bakar pun rasanya biasa saja. 
Kami sekeluarga kecewa, apalagi untuk harga yg cukup tinggi pada menu makanannya.
reviews.title: Mengecewakan

reviews.text: Restoran ini terletak di salah satu jalan utama di Balikpapan. Restoran lumayan besar. Pada jam makan siang, restoran ini sangat ramai, karena memang sajian iganya yang enak dan lumayan beragam. Pelayanan dalam penyajian makanan cepat dan efisien. Restoran ini mengenakan pajak 10% kepada pelanggan sesuai dengan Perda kota Balikpapan. Tetapi, apabila Anda tidak makan di restoran dan hanya takeaway, maka makanan yang Anda bungkus tersebut tidak dikenakan pajak. Menurut saya, walaupun hal kecil, tetapi sangat berkesan bagi saya. Owner restoran berlaku adil kepada pelanggannya. Saya baru kali ini menemukan 'small gesture' yang sangat baik seperti ini. Mudah-mudahan banyak restoran yang mencontoh praktek 'treat your customer right & fair the way you want to be treated'. Saya sangat menghargai upaya dari owner restoran ini. Akan menjadi tujuan tetap saya untuk bersantap setiap kali mengunjungi kota Balikpapan.
reviews.title: Enak, pelayanan jujur dan memuaskan

reviews.text:
Dekat dengan hotel kami menginap (whizz hotel) ketemulah tempat ini. Lokasinya cukup strategis di pinggir jalan raya. 
Saat itu kondisi sedang cukup ramai pengunjung namun kami terlayani dengan baik tanpa harus menunggu lama baik untuk memesan maupun menikmati makanan.
Kami memesan steak, nasi goreng dan tahu sebagai camilan.
Ternyata rasanya lumayan sesuai dengan yang harus dibayar.
reviews.title: Sesuai

reviews.text: Pas saya dateng tempat nya ramai pesen nya lama apa karena kebanyakan karyawan nya wanita.untuk rasa biasa saja dan harga terjangkau
reviews.title: Ramai saja

reviews.text: Enaknya ndak ngerti lg sudah, menu andalan kalau kesini pasti Paket Iga Penyet Goreng. Iga + nasi panas + sambal bawang pedas + kuah sup iga. Ampuuuun enaknya selalu bikin nagih, jauh2 ke Balikpapan dari Samarinda kalau lg pengen makan ini hihihi..
reviews.title: Simulasi surga dunia

reviews.text: Tanggal 31 des 2016 tepatnya pukul 18:24 wita, make order setelah menunggu kurang lebih 45 menit, pelayanan datang mengatakan kalau ang dipesen saat itu tongseng iga lagi kosong dan yang bikin miris pelayan mengatakan kalau pesanan yang lain baru akan dibuat, jadi minuman yang sudah dipesan dihemat hemat lagi karna nunggu makan terpaksa gua tinggal sehubungan sudah sakit hati ama pelayanannya. Pas bayar 60 ribu untuk minuman saja casir saya complain tapi bukannya minta maaf malah terima kasih aja gak. Jadi yang makan disini harus punya kesabaran tinggi maklum saya kalau lapar trus dengan pelayanan seperti itu bisa naik darah padahal belum makan tuh iganya.
reviews.title: Pelayanan buruk

reviews.text: Dihitung2 porsi makanan rata2 kecil. Makanan yg paketnya cuma dapat 1 nasi + iga 1 batang. Tempatnya strategis karena terletak dipinggir jalan raya tapi sayang kecewa banget karena mesti nunggu skitar hampir 30 menit untuk 1 iga & 1 porsi kangkung. Kurang worthed dari segi harga & service
reviews.title: Mahal, porsi sedikit, lama

reviews.text: Dlu Saya pernah Makan disini rasa makanan nya enak..  Tdi pesan chicken steak sayur nya kurang segar n iga steak pnya teman Saya agak keras...
reviews.title: Penurunan rasa...

name: Bubur Ayam Samarinda
address: Jl. Jend. A. Yani No. 50 RT 55, Balikpapan Indonesia

reviews.text: I like to eat here sometimes I took home the bubur ayam samarinda. And It will help if you feel sick, just eat bubur ayam and soon you will be better, base on my experience.
reviews.title: Always come back..again and again

reviews.text: I have eaten at this place since I studied at Junior High School. I think this place is a sustainable culinary business in Balikpapan. The food taste is extraordinary, especially for the "hati ampela" topping. They also opened a new branch at Balikpapan Baru. Try this Bubur Ayam if you visit Balikpapan or you will regret because you miss this food delicious taste.
reviews.title: One of Balikpapan ultimate culinaries

reviews.text:
Simply not your average bubur ayam/porridge with chicken. Simple place, at the mainstreet.
The broth was delicious, tomato adds up freshness, and the we also tried the iced coconut water with syrup, it was so refreshing.
Definitely coming again!
reviews.title: Not the one to be missed, tasty bubur ayam!

reviews.text: I ate when I was sick and I think it's very suitable for people who are sick . Because the food is very soft to the throat . thankyou Bubur Ayam Samarinda (:
reviews.title: the Food was Soft

reviews.text: The food is very unique and delicious, yet they don't vary the menu. The price is relatively cheap though. Great to enjoy local culinary, the place is not to big or comfy.
reviews.title: unique and delicious

reviews.text: Bubur Samarinda still good in my tasty mouth and tongue. Location is in central city. Although its name Bubur Samarinda, but i never try this porridge in Samarinda City. Because of this place is a popular foods, so it is not difficult to ask people all the city to find where.
reviews.title: Unique Porridge

reviews.text:
Not quite fond with this kind of porridge, the price is quite expensive when the taste is not really different with any other chicken porridge.
The service is not good but then its another cuisine that you have to tried for once
reviews.title: Just average

reviews.text:
the porridge was soupy with chicken broth.
A perfect meal during the flu attack. it was delicious.
Though the service is not really good.
reviews.title: not your average porridge..

reviews.text: Best porridge in town. Eat in at the Plaza Balikpapan whenever we visit Balikpapan. Tasty chicken porridge. Simply love it!
