reviews.text: There is little choice where to go for a beer in Balikpapan. Central location with outside beer garden, live music and good atmosphere. Food is ok but not good value for money. Good service. Recommended
reviews.title: Nice watering hole

reviews.text: This is a nice, centrally located bar in Balikpapan.  There is live music that gets the crowd involved.  The bar staff are very friendly and the beer nice and cold.  Pizzas are excellent and available all night long.  Indoor smoking is allowed which is a bit annoying but that is generally the norm over here.  Location is good with access from multiple hotels and the e-Walk mall as well as the Balikpapan Super Block.  It's a good place for a few beers and a feed with friends.  If there is one complaint it's that the beers are expensive, even local beers a lot more that what I am used to.
reviews.title: Good bar, friendly bartenders, excellent pizza and live music.

reviews.text:
This is a nice local pub 
Located right across from Grand Jatra Hotel 
They have amazing snacks for food, such as the Mozarella wings, the Pepperoni Pizza (its beef pepperoni by the way), the chicken wings and so much more 

They played soft and entertaining music through the evening 

But they started belting out the rock and other music much later (after we left the place) 

The beers were chilleeeeeedddddd and awesome 

Great selection, however all by bottle 
Erdinger by bottle, they had the white and the dark both, and a whole host of other local craft beers and of course the usual ones as well such as Heineken and Carlsberg are all available as part of the offering 

The staff is friendly and smiling and happy to serve and welcoming 

The toilets are sparkling clean and thats always a plus point for my consideration when I am at a pub or a bar 

Great place to hangout 
If you are in the area then please make a stop here
reviews.title: Nice local pub

reviews.text:
If you like a place for hang out then this is the place.

Live music from young musicians.
Food is so so, not that special but please find your sit in outside because
reviews.title: Good place with live music

photos.caption: Beef Lasagna just an ordinary lasagna

reviews.text:
This place opened last year as House of Beer, but, after an eventful Ramadan, when they were selling drinks and should not have been, it has now been renamed Home of Borneo.

It is one of the more popular haunts in Balikpapan (mainly due to limited choice and limited local customer understanding); the decor is good, modern and relatively comfortable.
The bench seats inside are high and make an average adult feel like a child again, with dangling legs, or, sit on the edge to touch the floor.

There is an indoor area and an outdoor area, the indoor area is better (in my opinion) because it has more comfortable furnishings, Air Conditioning and above all no noise and exhaust pollution due to hundreds of cars/vans passing by, to get to the 5* Jatra hotel or the Mal's car park and drop off area.

The real problem is the staff (with the management);
	The members of staff are not very efficient and are not very observant (there are a few exceptions).
	Service is generally slow, once busy, it is frustrating.
	The members of staff do not understand the basics of customer service, especially when something is wrong or the quality of item provided is well below par.
	As everyone in Balikpapan knows, it is hot here and never gets really cool; storage has to be considered a serious issue.
	Many times I have had Bintang beer that is off; the beer has clearly been 'cooked' by the sun, being stored outside, but the staff have no training and no knowledge of this common problem.
	When I have complained they are reluctant to change the bottle (at least 80% full), when the bottle is changed, they add it to your bill.
	My fiance has ordered fruit juice, where they serve juice that is clearly bad but cannot understand that freshness and quality is an issue; when the bill comes, a second juice is on the bill.

Food quality is average at best; the kitchen staff members (never mind service staff) show no pride in their products;
	I have eaten pizza (initially it was good, not so good now), but takes an average of 45 minutes to 1 hour to come.
	I have had a friend become seriously ill (vomiting and diarrhoea) after eating an HoB pizza.
	A lot of food is fried, but, it is not fried correctly; as it is served, it is swimming in discoloured oil, a clear sign of oil at too low a temperature and poor service/drainage of fried foods, as well as, bad oil changing practises.
	One night we asked for nachos, after waiting for an hour, we pushed.   The nachos arrived and were cold; we complained and any normal food business would replace the offending nachos (normally with double portions), we got our original ones back after 10 minutes having been put into a microwave and turned into extremely poor quality molten mush.
	There are many other examples

The biggest worry is honesty of the management and staff;
	At least six times (to my immediate knowledge), bills have been presented to customers where drinks are included that were never ordered or consumed.
	I have also heard of other customers being subject to this poor practise. 
	Normally there are two or three drinks (such as vodka and tonic) added to your bill.
	If you go there, be wary and check your bills.
	I include management in this evidence because the extra charges come on a bill, generated by the computer system, a system checked and managed by the management team (normally).

My friends still go there due to their need of a variety of establishments, and, I will occasionally join my friends there, but, if it was not for my friends, I would never give this company the honour of my presence again.
reviews.title: Nice decor, the rest needs work

photos.caption: Poor quality customer service and poor quality food, microwaved nachos after a complaint  :-(

name: Joy's Bar & Restaurant
address: Jl. Jend. Sudirman No. 33 RT 049, Balikpapan 76114 Indonesia

reviews.text: if you wants to get some drinks with friends, and many expats come here on friday & sat. on sat often really full.
reviews.title: Bar in the Mid of City

reviews.text: When I last visited Indonesia, I was pleased to see that Joy's had totally remodeled their bar, and updated their menu. This is one of the oldest expat hang outs in Balikpapan, and it is still going as strong as ever. They have live music on the weekends, and the food is decent bar food by Indonesian standards. The beer is served very cold, and with a smile.
reviews.title: Old establishment, new look

reviews.text: Joy's always been the preferred pub from the expat community in Balikpapan. Cold beer, decent food, good live bands and pool tables. After the refurbishing it looks like a sport bar and a lot of Aussies go there to watch Australian Football. The waitress will never let you have an empty beer bottle. Great place for a happy hour or Friday night drink.
reviews.title: Best pub in Balikpapan

reviews.text: Joy's Bar was a favorite spot but was marred by excess smoke.  However after a refurbishment it's a much more pleasant environment.  There's frequent live music, the food is good and the beer is cold.  Parking is a bit tricky but nothing you can't get around.  A great place for a beer and a feed, and even better when the footy is on.
reviews.title: Overhauled and all the better for it

reviews.text:
Joy's Bar, well known to the Expat community in Balikpapan had a refurbishment last Ramadan and has a kitchen capable of producing food for eating as a snack with drinks, or sitting down for a meal in their partitioned dining area.

They offer a variety of foods, Indonesian, basic Western foods and bar snacks.

Do not order food expecting an authentic style of food, as an example, the pizzas are not like you would find in Italy, but they are thin and tasty, great after a few beers to satisfy the munchies.

Several people have commented and I tend to agree that the burgers served at Joy's are the best burgers in Balikpapan.

Most nights, there is a band playing until the early hours.

It is busiest on Friday and Saturday nights, Saturday is often a themed party.
It gets busy after 22:00

When visiting Balikpapan (especially at the weekend), visit Joy's, there is always someone to talk to and the beer is always cold.
reviews.title: It is pub grub, but tasty and not expensive

photos.caption: Joy's Beef Burger with Cheese (already started to eat)

reviews.text: Joy's Bar merupakan salah 1 pub yang paling sering saya kunjungi di Balikpapan. Tempatnya nyaman dan tidak kotor, makanan dan minuman juga masih terjangkau dan enak rasanya. Musik yang diputar juga enak-enak, cocok untuk yang ingin hang out bersama teman
reviews.title: Pub Favorit

reviews.text:
Mungkin kalian penasaran dengan " Dugem Seperti Di Rumah Sendiri " Karena JOYS Bar Memiliki service yang sangat baik, mengganggap costumer Seperti layaknya keluarga Sendiri. Yang lebih penting dari semuanya minumanya tidak mahal hehheh. 

Love JOYS Bar
reviews.title: Dugem Seperti Di Rumah Sendiri

name: Konro Puncak
address: Jl. MT. Haryono, Balikpapan Indonesia

reviews.text:
As its name, u should go to the resto with amazing elevation 
Makes me scared at the beginning whether my car will slip or anything else. But its not, of course, just my thought 

Ordering the food, a little bit long to wait, remembering its a "soup". Even I have less time to wait at the original food comes from. 

But when the konro came, its just gone. The taste makes u forgot that u have waited. Sooo delicious 

The price itself is on average. 30k or 35k, I forgot, per position of konro soup.
reviews.title: Delicious One!

reviews.text: Located in the hill, go up at the street right after simpang raya resto. Came here for lunch and dinner, never fail me. Tasted great, perfect portion, cheap, clean, and neat. They only sell konro, with additional white rice, kerupuk, salted egg, and peanut. One bowl of konro cost 30k (exclude tax). Dont expect a good view even its located in the hill.
reviews.title: Came here never fail me

reviews.text: Located in a high land of balikpapan. But sorry to say,  the view not very interesting. So do the taste.
It was situated in the house terrace. It's clean and neat. The food is great. You can only eat one thing, KONRO.
reviews.title: A humble meal

reviews.text: restoran sop Konro serasa di rumahan dengan view Kota Balikpapan di malam hari, suasana ruang tamu di rumah sendiri, harganya standart, sayangnya jalanan menuju lokasi agak susah dan sepi.
reviews.title: Sop Konro View Kota Balikpapan

reviews.text: Konro puncak tempat makan sop konro dengan view deretan rumah di puncak balikpapan, rasanya enak, harganya standart sayang tempatnya sepi dan kurang penerangan
reviews.title: Konro puncak tempat makan dengan view puncak

reviews.text: Konro Puncak ini tempatnya sedikit masuk dan menanjak, tetapi Konro yang di sajikan di sini sangat menggugah selera dengan daging nya yang sangat empuk. View Konro Puncak di waktu malam sangatlah bagus karena kita bisa melihat kota balikpapan di malam hari.... Sangat di rekomendasikan bagi anda yang mwnyukai Konro...
reviews.title: Tempat Makan Konro dengan view Balikpapan

reviews.text:
Lokasinya agak susah dijangkau karena masuk gang yang hanya muat 1 mobil terus naik ke atas bukit dari jalan utama agak curam..makany namanya konro puncak, karena memang dipuncak bukit..Parkiran mobilnya pun agak terbatas tapi tiap kali makan kesini dijam makan siang gak pernah kesusahan cari parkir..Meja & kursinya tersusun di teras rumah (infonya rumah kosan) dan kita harus lepas alas kaki..jadi bener2 kayak makan di teras rumah sendiri..
Kayakny menu disini cuma ada konro aja, minumnya air mineral, es teh, es jeruk (kayaknya gak ada jus) soalnya gak ada buku menu & pelayannya cuma nawarin 2 hal itu aja..dimeja makannya ada kerupuk, emping, telur asin, kacang goreng..bisa buat cemilan sambil nunggu konro-nya datang..tapi ini gak gratis ya..jangan lupa bilang ke kasirnya waktu bayar nanti..kunjungan terakhir saya tanggal 1 februari 2017 dan sangat mungkin untuk berkunjung lagi karena rasanya enak.
reviews.title: Sensasi makan di teras rumah

name: Bombay Curry Resto & Cafe
address: Ruko Bandar Kompleks Blok E-12A Ruko Bandar, Blok E - 12A,Klandasan Ulu, Balikpapan 76112 Indonesia

reviews.text: The ambiance is good, hygienic,as an Indian i expected Indian as server but no to my surprise its was Indonesian,which does compromised the knowledge on dishes and restro suggestions, the main part was food was okish , its not like as authentic as in India which was worst part
reviews.title: It was an okish restaurant

reviews.text: Ordered food from this place . Very nice Indian vegetarian food loved it thanks Food was tasty can try to make it more taste like North Indian , but good to have it in Balikpapan
reviews.title: Good vegetarian indian food  tasty

reviews.text: Came here for dinner last night. Food was okay. Different to what I am personally used to getting in Aus. Can be quite pricey. Some dishes are better than others.
reviews.title: Pleasant dinner

reviews.text: Visited this place for dinner on Tuesday.  Ordered biryani, paneer masala  -- nothing like it,  doesn't look or taste or smell like it. I have to believe that this chef has never eaten Indian in their life, let alone cook. . I am so surprised other reviewers had given this place good reviews,  I took a cab to this place after reading these reviews - what a waste!
reviews.title: Nothing like Indian cuisine

reviews.text: The Bombay curry House is authentic Indian restaurant in Balikpapan. The ambiance and light hindi music give a feel of typical Indian restaurant. I had vegetarian food there and the taste was really good. It's reasonably priced with fast service. It's not easy to find the location so I advise to use GPS to reach there.
reviews.title: Tasty Indian food

reviews.text:
Access : hard to find but still ok if you use gps
Food : great taste of curry... So much spices in one bite... Try their recommendation by asking the waitress
Price : Medium (50.000-100.000)
Service : very good, they give more water before you ask,place was clean n comfy feels like home..
reviews.title: So much taste in on bite

reviews.text: The Bombay curry House in Balikpapan is a very clean restaurant offering good choices for Vegetarians. I have tried the Dal Makhni, Baingan masala, Nauratan Kurma....all are good in taste. The portions may be less for 2 people. The place has a look and feel of India with nice Hindi music. Overall a boon for Vegetarians like me who have limited options in Balikpapan.
reviews.title: A heaven for Vegetarians

reviews.text: A very comfortable place, quite and cozy. Bombay Curry House serves many authentic Indian food and beverage on the house. The tastes are very good but the price is not that friendly. One of Balikpapan culinary spot.
reviews.title: Authentic Indian cuisine

reviews.text: terdapat banyak makanan khas india di tempat ini, rasanya enak dan stafnya yang ramah dalam melayani
reviews.title: masakan khas india

reviews.text: Suasana benar benar hommy. Rasa masakan luar biasa enak. Meski tempatnya sedikit tersembunyi,tapi buat pecinta kuliner India wajib dikunjungi
reviews.title: Masakan India di Balikapapan

reviews.text:
Datang dan cobalah, anda akan merasakan sendiri bagaimana aslinya masakan India di tempat ini, Tandoori Murg, Chicken Tikka, Rogan Gosht dan aneka macam Roti India ( Paratha, Naan, Chapatti, Puri dll )
Yang cari Vegetarian ala India, di sini tempatnya...........
reviews.title: Alternatif Masakan India di Balikpapan

photos.caption: Bombay Curry House is Original Indian Foods

name: Amplang Karya Utama Kita
address: 401, Jalan Jend. A. Yani, Balikpapan Indonesia

reviews.text: tempat oleh oleh di balikpapan yang recomended banget, terutama jika mencari amplang. bisa bebas mencari ukuran kemasan baik besar maupun kecil, yang enak rasa merica. bisa dicoba dulu kok
reviews.title: oleh oleh khas balikpapan

reviews.text: Salah satu amplang favorit saya di Balikpapan. Rasa yang ditawarkan beragam, bawang, merica, dan original. Pilihan kemasan juga bisa disesuaikan kebutuhan. Pembelanjaan akan dikemas dalam kardus apabila mencapai jumlah tertentu.
reviews.title: Banyak Ukuran Kemasan

reviews.text: kalau mau cari oleh-oelh kesini aja, letaknya di jalan Ahmad Yani, tempatnya paling deket dengan putar balik, harga bervariasi , untuk amplang ada 3 rasa; original, bawang dan merica
reviews.title: oleh-oleh khas balikpapan

reviews.text: Jika Anda ingin membawa pulang oleh"kas balikpapan tempat ini cukup mewakili baik dari variasi rasa dan pilihan paket besar atau kecil. Cukup bagi trip lover singgah di tempat ini. Salam trip lover.
reviews.title: Buah tangan trip lover Ampalang

reviews.text: Oleh oleh khas balikpapan. Amplang tiga rasa bawang, original, dan merica. Bisa mencicipi dulu sebelum beli. Rekomendasi rasa bawang dan merica. Oh ya ikan terasa banget. Salamtriptrip
reviews.title: Toko amplang tiga rasa

reviews.text: saya memilih amplang ini karena rasanya sedap, terasa ikannya, dan lokasi counternya masih di tengah kota. ampalngnya selalu baru, renyah dan cocok untuk dibawa pulang sebagai oleh2
reviews.title: amplangnya sedap, terasa ikannya

reviews.text:
ini dia camilan khas kalimantan.
saya suka banget Amplang.
rasanya mirip seperti kerupuk ikan.
kalo makan pasti nggak mau berhenti.
sebungkus pasti kurang.
kalo dari kalimantan, makanan/camilan ini wajib jadi oleh-oleh yang mesti di bawah pulang
reviews.title: oleh-oleh khas kalimantan

reviews.text: oleh-oleh khas balikpapan. krupuk yang terbuat dari ikan tenggiri. rasanya lezat dan renyah. saya lebih menyukai jenis yang agak pedas. krupuk cumi juga layak untuk dicoba. penjualnya akan dengan senang hati mempacking belanjaan kita
reviews.title: khas balikpapan

name: Kemala Beach & Resto
address: Jl. Jendral Sudirman, Balikpapan 76614 Indonesia

reviews.text: Used to be my favorite place to spend weekend night in Balikpapan. It feels like Bali when you come here. With live music and minimum light by the sea, it is hard to beat the location of this place. Unfortunately, no food can be recommended from this place. But at least the coconut is the same. Price is still OK.
reviews.title: Balikpapan's Bali

reviews.text: Makanan utk sekelas resto harganya sama dgn hotel *4 air putih hangat 10K dgn service jd. 11K atau 11.5K yg di hotel gratis.sementara rasa makanan B aja alias biasa aja.cuma menang tempat aja...
reviews.title: Air putih hangat 10K++

reviews.text: pelayanan kurang baik, kurang tanggap, seperti tidak di layani dan dibiarkan saja karna ramai seharusnya bisa di bagi dan tidak berkerumun di situ saja
reviews.title: Kritik dan saran

reviews.text: Salah satu pantai di kota balikpapan ini terletak di belakang ditsabhara polda kaltim jadi tidak heran dipantai ini banyak anggota kepolisian. Suasananya cukup nyaman. Jika malam hari (mugkin malam tertentu) ada live musicnya. Kebetulan pas saya datang kesini ada live musicnya dan kamipun tidak ketinggalan untuk menyumbangkan lagu.
reviews.title: Menikmati kedai dipinggir pantai

reviews.text: berkunjung kerumah makan ini serasa di bali suasananya. rumah makan dengan view pantai di iringi alunan musik. mantap banget.
reviews.title: nuansa bali

reviews.text: Tempat yang bagus bgt, pelayanannya juga ramah. Makanannya enak bgt. Pokoknya ngga nyesel deh . Hehe
reviews.title: View bagus bgt

reviews.text: Pantai Kemala menjadi pilihan favorit warga Balikpapan untuk menghabiskan liburan akhir pekan,Menu yang ditawarkan  merupakan aneka kuliner dari bermacam - macam daerah dan masakan Khas Eropa.
reviews.title: menikmati keindahan pantai sambil menikmati menu - menu spesial

photos.caption: wajib coba udang gala lada hitam

reviews.text: Cocok untuk santai di dekat pantai, makanan lumayan enak dan bervariasi. Pegawainya ramah ramah dan menyediakan tempat untuk ulang tahun dan acara gathering. Keep up a good work!!
reviews.title: Nice place like Bali

reviews.text: Tempat makan sejenis food court, ada beberapa pilihan yang tersedia, agaknya harus pintar memilih salah satu dari sekian banyak pilihan. Suasana langsung berpijak dengan pasir-pasir, taman ditengah, bangku bangku taman tanpa sandaran dari kayu, terakhir saya datang ada canopy. my thumbs can't handle for the excelent view
reviews.title: Clean sand for walk, nice bench for sit

reviews.text: cocok untuk santap malam sembari menikmati matahari terbenam,  pelayanan ramah, menu variatif, lokasi mudah dijangkau
reviews.title: restoran keren di pinggir pantai

reviews.text: Restoran ini letaknya di pantai Kemala, sebenarnya lokasi sangat bagus karena persis di tepi pantai. Makanannya juga cukup enak dan harganya pun cukup terjangkau. Namun sayangnya tempatnya kurang terpelihara dengan baik, sebut saja kolam di dalam restoran sangat kotor dan airnya berwarna hitam, daun-daun kering bertebaran dimana-mana. Pelayanannya sih cukup baik.
reviews.title: Makanan enak, view pantai bagus tapi sayangnya tempatnya kurang terpelihara dengan baik

reviews.text: Restaurant yang Berada Pinggir Pantai, Tempat wisata untuk bersama Keluarga,  dan Pasir Pantai Yang Bersih.
reviews.title: Memiliki View di Pinggir Pantai, dan Berada Tepat DI Tengah Kota Balikpapan

name: RM Ujung Pandang
address: Jln. Pranoto APT 5/21, Balikpapan 76112 Indonesia

reviews.text: tempat makan yang menyajikan khas makassar, tapi sayang tidak semuanya ada seperti es palu butung, cobain coto makassarnya rasanya lumayan enak.
reviews.title: coto makassar nya enak

reviews.text: salah satu rumah makan khas makassar, cobain menu coto makassar yang gurih, sup konro yang nikmat dan es pisang hijau yang segar dan manis.
reviews.title: rumah makan khas makassar

reviews.text: Ternyata bagi kita yang pingin menikmati cita rasa masakan Sulsel di Balikapapan, tempat ini sangat recommended. Saya suka dengan Sop Konro dan Mie pangsitnya. Lezat seperti di Makassar.
reviews.title: Makassarnya Balikpapan

reviews.text: Mencari rumah makan khas Makassar atau Ujung Pandang di kota Balikpapan juga tidak terlalu sulit, karena banyaknya pendatang dari Sulawesi Selatan yang tinggal di Balikpapan. Di rumah makan ini, saya dapat menikmati sop konro yang lezat, mie pangsit Ujung Pandang, maupun coto Makassar.
reviews.title: Sop Konro-nya sangat pantas dinikmati

reviews.text: Anda pernah dengar Coto Makassar, disinilah kita akan temukan rasa Coto Makassar yang istimewa. Gurih dan Kental kuahnya. Bikin kita ketagihan
reviews.title: Khas Makassar

name: D' Sushi
address: Jl. Jendral Sudirman no. 16, Balikpapan 76112 Indonesia

reviews.text:
First the place, the ambience is like any other restaurant. But the AC wasn't working well, I  got enough sweat as I sat for an hour there, and they played some hiphop and rnb songs throughout the night. I don't think it goes well with the theme. 

Second the waitresses, they didn't greet us  neither sat us on our table. We stood and lost for a moment there, and they like don't know how to politely put the menus, nor the setting the meals on our table.
I ordered an iced ocha, and it came after my second meals. 
But the waitresses are kind when you asked around about the meals. 

And finally the sushi and other foods. I ordered chuka idako, kitsune sushi, salmon nigiri, and chawan mushi. But none of them exceeded my expectations. The idako baby squids textured like liver, while it should be squishy. The sushis were fine, and the chawan mushi wasn't great. 

I don't think I want to pay that much for those meals and services. It costs me around 180 thousand rupiahs for those meals. And I can get the taste I wanted with better service at sushiya or sushitei.
reviews.title: So so~

reviews.text: On this month i already come third time to this place, me and my wife only like the chicken little roll, and i try the niku katsudon. The taste is always change, is like doesnt have a SOP on the kitchen,even for the sushi its always change. And the last time i come the texture of the beef on katsudon its worst. Almost the same taste with liver.Maybe the beef to long in the freezer or chiller. you need to improve ,because this is japanese restaurant,please give attention to your material is always fresh and the quality of all your product
reviews.title: Improve the quality control of food

reviews.text:
The place is good. They provide 'normal' chair seating as well as in tatami style.
The menu is varied, recently, they even provide Crab!

The sushi is mainly fusion with OK taste.
The sashimi quality is improving recently.
The service is improving, particularly when the boss is around.. ;)
The price, a bit pricey.
reviews.title: One of the best-available sushi in Balikpapan

reviews.text:
The place is clean and welcoming. The personnel has improved since they open.
The Sushi are not always fresh and this is my main concern. They add tube mayonnaise on the top of most of the sushi that do not help the freshness.
Overall this is ok but not the best place for a nice sushi dinner.
reviews.title: Not the best sushi....

reviews.text:
Come with family for dinner and having a good ambience, friendly staff. Misi soup was bad, but sushi is very good. Price was so expensive.

Staff was asking about the comment and we told about the bad miso. That's all.
reviews.title: Expensive but worth the price

reviews.text:
Visited on a weekday evening for dinner. No complaints.
Overall it was a pretty good meal. The standard of the food was good, as was the ambience. The main let-down was the slow service.
reviews.title: The Food and Ambience was good but slow service

reviews.text: The sushi are not always good and fresh. The quality varies every day. The service is poor. No alcohol.
reviews.title: Sushi in Balikpapan

reviews.text: Do not put the high expectation if you want to get a japanese food in here. The taste is not typical japanese. The rice is too hard sometimes. The sashimi is not fresh. Once I ordered the salmon skin fried and it was really hard. Not recommended for a japanese food lovers
reviews.title: Average

reviews.text:
I am not really fan of japanese foods. But I could say the ramen was killed it! It has big portion and I have to share it with my friend.

This restaurant was really easy to find
 If you are in Balikpapan and love japanese foods. You should come here to try the ramen.
reviews.title: Very good, value for money

reviews.text: the taste average, and everyday this restaurany always full customers, perhaps this place is one of cheap sushi resto in Balikpapan.
reviews.title: D'Sushi..the 1st Sushi house in Balikpapan

reviews.text: This resto is not recommended for the real japanese food lover. I have tried their ramen, sashimi and cawan mushi. I could not taste typical japanese spices and the they should learn how to preserve the fish(es) for sushi.
reviews.title: Definietely not a Japanese Taste

reviews.text: first try, after a month it was founded. The place is very comfortable, but the service of this place is less satisfactory. For about the price does have a cheaper price than class sushi restaurant. However, in terms of taste is less satisfying. If I say there is a sense there is a price.
reviews.title: Cheap price according to taste

reviews.text: My daughters are sushi maniacs and I frequently take them to D'Sushi. They have a good variety of sushis & sashimis. The fish is always fresh. Besides the sushis they have a good variety of japanese dishes. The prices are good, so it's a real value for money.
reviews.title: Best sushis in Balikpapan

reviews.text:
I went with my girlfriend, she wanted to go, but I was not too enthusiastic to begin (I prefer Korean food).

We went on a Sunday afternoon around 14.30, there were one or two people there, but it was not too busy.

We had Salmon Carpaccio, Tuna Sushi (seared with a blow torch), Udon noodles with beef, 1/2 Dory fish, grilled with vegetables, Japanese salad with raw fish, some type of egg starter and 2 types of tea.

I will not bore you with the smaller details, but it was very good, excellent value for money and highly enjoyable.  It was below Rp300,000 for the both of us.

The quality of the food was very good, i thoroughly enjoyed it.

I will happily return to this restaurant.
reviews.title: Very good value for money

reviews.text: Saat ke Balikpapan dan ingin menikmati sushi silakan datang ke D'Sushi. Pilihan menu sushi nya lumayan beragam, rasa sushinya walaupun bukan yang paling enak di Balikpapan, tapi lumayan untuk sekedar mencicipi masakan Jepang di Balikpapan
reviews.title: Suhsi standard tapi worth it

reviews.text:
Masakannya bertambah variasinya dibandingkan saat awal-awal buka. 
Ada aburi soba dan menu dessert baru.
Suasananya masih sama seperti awal-awal buka, demikian juga dengan layanannya masih cukup bagus.
reviews.title: Aburi Soba menu baru di de Sushi Balikpapan

reviews.text: Rasa sushi lumayan, Ramen sedikit terlalu matang sehingga jadi lembek. Chicken teriyaki rasanya biasa. Lumayan, untuk menghibur kita yang sedang rindu masakan japanese.
reviews.title: Dinner

reviews.text:
My Favorite japanesse food di balikpapan. 
Fair price. Ramah waitersnya, sayang kadang A.C nya ga kurang dingin. 
Moga di improve dan diganti dgn AC central atau kapasitas lebih besar. 
Salmonnya luar biasa dibanding tuna.
reviews.title: Mampir untuk kesekian kalinya

reviews.text:
Makan siang sama adik saya di De'sushi. Gak nyesal deh kesini ^^ makanannya enak dan beragan macam. Sampai bingug mau pesan apa. Jd pengen ke sini lagi nyobain menu lain. Untuk kunjungan pertama ini saya memesan chiken teriyaki roll dan chocolate smoothies. Dan adik saya memesan chiken miso ramen dan vanilla smoothies :) karena pengen yg lain jg saya pesan dibungkus gyoza dan salmon nigiri. Hehe.. Biar gak kepuhunan. Kalau ke de sushi gk bs sekali, harus berkali-kali biar bisa ngerasain semua menunya :D jgn lupa siapin uang saku lebih.

Yang kurang menurut saya pelayanannya yg terkadang ngeliatin kita makan dan ada jg ekspresinya cemberut gitu. Dr segi pelayanan bagus, tp ya sikapnya yg kurang :")
reviews.title: Makan siang

reviews.text: O restaurante em si de japons s o nome. Os sushis, apesar de criativos e de uma carta bastante ampla, nao sao muito apetitosos. A apresentao  justa para o preo do prato, mas as bebidas deixam a desejar pela qualidade

reviews.text: het is een eenvoudig restaurant aan de doorgaande weg, dicht bij het vliegveld. De ambiance is eenvoudig; je zit er op eenvoudige stoeltjes aan eenvoudige tafeltjes. Daar zit je samen met de lokale bevolking. Dus als je wilt genieten(!) van de lokale keuken, moet je deze Pondok n Pondok Ikan Bakar Asia zeker bezoeken. reviews.text:
Recommended milk tea : Belgium chocolate milk tea, avocado milk tea & almond milk tea. Smoothies : Belgium chocolate smothies.
Pilihan topping lumayan banyak.

reviews.text: salah satu minuman favorit saya, asik diminum saat cuaca panas menyengat. ada rasa yakult jadi segar segar asam, tapi kurang enak jika rencana nongkrong disini.
reviews.title: smoothiesnya segar banget

reviews.text: Seperti halnya gerai waralaba yang menjual minuman milk tea, gerai Teapresso juga menyajikan minuman yang segar, dengan pilihan topping yang beragam. Sangat menyejukkan diminum dikala hari panas.
reviews.title: Milk tea yang segar dikala panas

reviews.text: Untuk buka puasa, saya membeli smoothies disini. Saya memesan Green Apple Yakult Smoothies. Untuk Smoothiesnya cukup segar karena kombinasi apel hijau dengan yakult. Namun untuk pearl kali ini cukup keras buat saya. Selebihnya cukup nikmat untuk pembuka puasa.
reviews.title: Smoothies segar, pearl relatif keras kali ini

reviews.text: Seperti chatime t menunya.biasa aja rasanya.nggak ada yg special.letaknya di mall.buat nongkrong juga kuang enak....

reviews.text:
Teh yang unik, meski diimpor dari Taiwan. namun cukup kreatif dengan campuran yang bervariasi.
Lokasi yang mudah dijangkau, namun susah untuk mencar tempat duduk. Tidak cocok untuk nongkrong.
reviews.title: Teh Taiwan

reviews.text: Setelah makan siang, saya kesini untuk makanan penutup. Hari masih cukup terang dan saya perhatikan gerai teapresso ini sedang mempersiapkan diri untuk melayani. Setelah cukup siap, menurut mereka, saya kemudian memesan taro smoothies dengan topping original pearl. Sedikit tidak biasa disini, ketika saya memesan ukuran reguler, pelayan mengucapkan sudah habis, meski baru saja buka di siang hari??. Habis atau tidak disediakan memiliki makna yang berbeda. Jika memang tidak ada, alangkah bijaknya jika diucapkan tidak tersedia bukan. Tapi yang pasti, taro smoothies yang saya beli cukup segar, ditambah dengan  topping pearlnya yang banyak.
reviews.title: Taro Smoothies nya enak, sayang semua ukuran gelas tak tersedia meski hari masih siang

reviews.text: Saya kembali mencoba smoothies disini. Cukup pagi kesini dan segera saya memesan strawberry smoothies dengan topping pearl. Ukuran gelas besar dipilih. Sekitar dua puluh tujuh ribu rupiah digunakan untuk menebus pesanan. Di teapresso ini, smoothiesnya padat dan jumlah toppingnya relatif banyak. Saya setuju smoothies disini, porsinya cukup banyak untuk ukuran smoothies dibandingkan dengan tipe gerai yang sama.
reviews.title: Smoothiesnya padat

name: BreadTalk
address: Jl. MT Haryono No 1 Giant Extra MT Haryono, Balikpapan 76114 Indonesia

reviews.text: Jenisnya cukup banyak dan jenisnya enak rnak, saya suka sekali dengan jenis roti sosis dan blueberry chesse cakenya, dan selalu fresh

reviews.text: Selalu suka dengan roti ini dan selalu ada pembaruan menu baik itu di BreadTalk BPN maupun JKT. Harga cukup bersahabat.

reviews.text: lokasinya di dalam supermatket giant sehingga memudahkan pembelinya. tidak ada yang special dari toko roti ini, sama saja seperti cabang breadtalk lainnya. Karena mungkin brand Breadtalk menerapkan SOP yang sama untuk semua cabangnya.
reviews.title: Sama saja seperti cabang breadtalk lainnya

reviews.text: suka banget sama menu dan presentasi dari bread talk, rasa coklat yang tidak terlalu manis saya suka, suka banget sama roti bertabur abonnya

reviews.text: Saya membeli blueberry choco milk, choco raisin dan satu kue lagi untuk cemilan disini. Cemilan kenyang saya menyebutnya. Selain kenyang, enak dan renyah serta manis, layanan disini cukup ramah sehingga menambah lembut kue yang dijual. Saya tidak bisa komentar lebih banyak lagi.
reviews.title: Layanan ramah untuk kue yang lembut

name: New Star Kopitiam
address: Jln. Jendral Sudirman Balikpapan Superblock E. Walk Mall Lt. I, Balikpapan 76114 Indonesia

reviews.text: New Star Kopitiam is located in the basement floor of Ewalk Shopping Mall in Balikpapan Super Block. They serve asian cuisine along with variety of coffee. Foods taste OK, nothing special. Interior simple retro classic, dominated by wooden walls and meubelair with accents of retro pictures. Cleanliness was good. It gives different experience to eat in this restaurant.
reviews.title: Classic retro cuisine

reviews.text: Rasa masakan tidak bisa dibilang istimewa atau unik, tetapi atmosfer tempat ini menjadi salah satu pertimbangan untuk kembali lagi kesini. Dari pertama mencoba resto ini, belum ada hidangan yang membuat saya ingin memesan kembali (entah itu terlalu asin, terlalu hambar) sehingga setiap kesini selalu mencoba hidangan yang lain. tetapi untuk hang out dengan teman memang pas karena ada wifi. Harga standar Balikpapan.
reviews.title: pilihan makan di BSB

name: Gado-Gado Siram Persiba
address: Jl. Warukin Persiba Stadium, Balikpapan Indonesia

reviews.text: Located beside PERSIBA stadium and near some working places, offices and high populated areas makes this stall quite popular. It is only a simple place but quite comfort to stay there. One makes special of it is the generous portion you will have compared to the money you paid. The taste also great. They serves the salad freshly with additional soy cake (tahu, tempe) and boiled egg. The unusual is the cut of the salads, the have it big. I also like the peanut sauce. It is not too thick, fresh, balance in taste and for sure in generous number, don't hesitate to have more just by asking. It is favorite of mine and my colleagues.
reviews.title: Favorite Gado-Gado

name: Warung Segeri
address: Jl. Letjend. Suprapto, Balikpapan Indonesia

reviews.text:
Setiap kali ke BPN sy pasti makan di rm ini. Rm nya sgt sederhana tp ikannya fresh dan murah sekali. Disediakan byk jenis sambal termasuk sambel kacang dan sambal mangga yg paling sy suka.
Favorit sy ikan bandeng dibakar, tidak dibelah (khas bakarannya shg minyak ikannya keluar dan yg hangus hny kulit ikannya).

reviews.text: menikmati panti kurang lengkap jika tidak menikmati hidangan lautnya, jarajnya cuma beberapa puluh meter dari pantai yang anda kunjungi (pantai monpera) tersedia berbagai jenis pilihan
reviews.title: Pilihan makanan seafood dipesisir Balikpapan

reviews.text:
nama segeri adalah nama daerah di daerah maros sulawesi selatan yang terenal dengan daerah tambak ikannya untuk itu tentunya harapan yang saya bawa adalah menikmati ikan segar dengan bumbu sambal makassar.
kami datang ke warung segeri atas rekomendasi keluarga di balikpapan, tempatnya mudah dijangkau karena berada di samping monumen balikpapan (pusat kota) dan  berada di pinggir pantai serta memiliki parkir yang luas.
kami memesan beberapa jenis ikan yang sebagin kami bakar dan atas rekomendasi dari pelayan kami direkomendasikan memesan ikan Baronang asam manis.
kesan pertama kami adalah warung segeri bereda dengan warung ikan bakar khas makassar di makassar yang biasanya menyediakan beberapa macam sambal dan kita melakukan pencampuran sesuai selera, dimeja hanya tersedia satu jenis sambal saja berbeda dengan warung ikan bakar khas makassar.
tidak ada otak otak seagai hidangan pembuka jadi kami hanya menunggu tersajinya makanan dengan berbincang bincang (padahal kami menunggu sekitar 45 menit... sayang tanpa ada cemilan)  
saat memesan minuman hampir semua juice kosong (kecuali juice timun) kami hanya memesan es teh dan teh manis (hanya ini yang ada) 
saat hidangan datang kami disajikan sejenis sambal tomat dan saat kami tanya jenis smabal lain ternyata tidak ada, ikan yang disajikan segar namun khusus untuk ikan asam manis penyajiannya tidak sesuai harapan kami dimana saos yang digunakan adalah jenis saos murah yang membuat warna saos cenderung hitam dan terlalu manis .. ikan tidak di fillet namun klangsung di goreng utuh dan ditaburi saos 
secara rasa kami menilai untuk ikan bakarnya cukup enak, sambalnya kurang variasi sedangkan untuk ikan asam manis perlu perbaikan di rasa dan cara presentasi.
untuk pelayanan terlalu lambat padahal kami datang pada saat meja hanya terisi dua (termasuk meja kami)
reviews.title: Berbeda dengan Harapan

reviews.text: Terletak di daerah Kampung Baru, warung ini seudah lama terkenal dengan menu ikan bakar dan hidangan lautnya seperti cumi-cumi dan udang. Bahan-bahanya segar dan sambal tomatnya memang tidak bisa ditemukan di tempat lain.
reviews.title: Fresh Ikan Bakar

reviews.text: Sambal khas Bugis + Bandeng Goreng di tambah Cumi goreng tepung nya bener-bener TOP BANGET! Di tambah hidangan Sup Palu mara khas makasar! Tidak ada lawan nya Miiiii!! Terbaik ini jiiiii
reviews.title: Sambal terbaik
